nforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20case%20related%20to%20the%20now-scrapped%20liquor%20policy.%C2%A0The%20bench%20of%20Justice%20Swarana%20Kanta%20Sharma%20has%20passed%20over%20the%20matter%20for%20a%20hearing%20later%20in%20the%20day%20after%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20counsel%2C%20Senior%20Advocate%20Abhishek%20Singhvi%20questioned%20the%20agency's%20%26quot%3Bdelaying%20tactics%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAppearing%20for%20the%20ED%2C%20Additional%20Solicitor%20General%20SV%20Raju%20said%20the%20agency%20got%20a%20copy%20of%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20petition%20only%20yesterday%20and%20sought%20three%20weeks'%20time%20to%20file%20a%20detailed%20reply.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singhvi%20responded%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20person%20has%20been%20jail.%20On%20March%2023%2C%20the%20petition%20was%20filed.%20Defects%20were%20cured%20later.%20I%20am%20sure%20Mr%20Raju%20does%20not%20want%20us%20to%20serve%20the%20defective%20copy%20to%20him.%20Defects%20were%20cleared%20late%20last%20night%20and%20we%20shared%20the%20petition%20with%20him%20then.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Sharma%20then%20said%20she%20will%20seek%20a%20reply%20and%20give%20a%20short%20date%20for%20the%20hearing%20on%20interim%20relief.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singhvi%20said%20he%20has%20challenged%20the%20remand%20that%20ends%20tomorrow.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20asking%20the%20ladyship%20to%20decide%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20remand.%20That%20requires%20no%20reply%20from%20anyone.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20delaying%20tactics%2C%20I%20am%20asking%20my%20ladyships%20to%20decide%20it%20today.%20There%20are%20weighty%20reasons%20why%20a%20matter%20which%20challenges%20the%20foundation%20of%20the%20remand%20requires%20a%20hearing%20today.%20It%20is%20my%20ladyship's%20prerogative%20to%20allow%20it%20or%20deny%20it.%20My%20ladyship%20may%20take%20a%20call%20on%20that.%20Therefore%2C%20there%20is%20no%20question%20of%20reply%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20has%20said%20in%20his%20petition%20that%20his%20arrest%20violated%20his%20human%20rights%20and%20that%20the%20ED%20has%20failed%20to%20prove%20the%20crime.%20%26quot%3BArrest%20without%20interrogation%20shows%20that%20the%20current%20action%20is%20politically%20motivated%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20has%20said%2C%20demanding%20immediate%20release%20from%20jail%20and%20cancellation%20of%20remand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20then%20said%20it%20will%20hear%20the%20matter%20later%20in%20the%20day%20after%20finishing%20the%20supplementary%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20court%20started%20hearing%20the%20matter%2C%20Mr%20Singhvi%20said%20the%20ED's%20request%20for%20three%20weeks'%20time%20is%20%26quot%3Bcompletely%20mala%20fide%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BEven%20one%20day%20incarceration%20is%20an%20issue%20of%20fundamental%20right%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20strange%20situation%20of%20a%20sitting%20CM%20arrested%20on%20a%20summons%20issued%20in%20October%20without%20any%20statement%20under%20Section%2050%20and%20non-existent%20inquiry.%20The%20object%20of%20the%20arrest%20is%20very%20different.%20It%20is%20to%20create%20a%20non-level%20playing%20field%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20are%20hitting%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20democracy%20and%20the%20heart%20of%20basic%20structure%20doctrine%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singhvi%20said%20the%20ED%20arrests%20a%20person%2C%20who%20suffers%20in%20jail%20and%20is%20then%20made%20to%20apply%20for%20bail.%20%26quot%3BNext%20step%2C%20the%20ASG%20tells%20the%20court%20I%20have%20no%20opposition%20to%20bail.%20The%20reason%20cited%20is%20he%20has%20back%20pain.%20The%20next%20step%20is%2C%20he%20comes%20out%20and%20makes%20a%20statement%20against%20me.%20Next%20he%20turns%20approver%20and%20is%20granted%20pardon%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20has%20happened%20in%20every%20case%20in%20the%20liquor%20policy%20case.%20It%20is%20blowing%20to%20smithereens%20the%20constitutional%20safeguards%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singhvi%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20there%20is%20no%20corroboration%20of%20these%20statements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDescribing%20an%20approver%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bmost%20untrustworthy%20friend%26quot%3B%2C%20Mr%20Singhvi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20species%20called%20approver...%20In%20our%20history%2C%20whether%20for%20good%20motives%20or%20bad%20motives%2C%20the%20courts%20have%20dealt%20with%20phrases%20like%20Jaichand%20and%20Trojan%20Horses.%20The%20history%20looks%20very%20harshly%20at%20these%20Jaichands%20and%20Trojan%20horses.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20ED's%20counsel%20SV%20Raju%20said%20he%20wants%20to%20file%20replies%20on%20the%20main%20matter%20and%20on%20the%20petition%20for%20interim%20relief.%20When%20the%20court%20said%20it%20has%20already%20said%20that%20it%20will%20issue%20notice%20in%20the%20main%20matter%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOn%20interim%20relief%20also%2C%20I%20have%20the%20right%20to%20file%20a%20reply.%20If%20I%20am%20not%20entitled%20to%20file%20a%20reply%2C%20then%20there%20is%20no%20need%20to%20hear%20me.%20I%20can't%20be%20deprived%20of%20my%20right%20to%20file%20a%20reply.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20then%20said%20it%20will%20pass%20and%20order%20by%204%20pm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20day%20after%20his%20arrest%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20had%20approached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20for%20relief.%20However%2C%20he%20later%20withdrew%20his%20petition%20and%20his%20counsel%2C%20Senior%20Advocate%20Abhishek%20Singhvi%2C%20said%20they%20would%20contest%20the%20remand%20proceedings%20before%20the%20trial%20court%20and%20return%20to%20the%20top%20court%20with%20another%20petition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThereafter%2C%20he%20was%20produced%20before%20the%20Rouse%20Avenue%20court%2C%20which%20remanded%20him%20in%20a%20weeklong%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED's%20money%20laundering%20case%20is%20based%20on%20a%20case%20registered%20by%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20in%202022%20that%20alleged%20irregularities%20in%20the%20liquor%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20case%2C%20registered%20on%20a%20complaint%20by%20Delhi's%20Centre-appointed%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20VK%20Saxena%2C%20alleges%20that%20top%20AAP%20leaders%20intentionally%20left%20loopholes%20in%20the%20policy%20to%20favour%20some%20licensees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20alleges%20that%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20was%20a%20key%20conspirator%20in%20the%20case.%20AAP%20leaders%20Manish%20Sisodia%20and%20Sanjay%20Singh%2C%20and%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20leader%20K%20Kavitha%20have%20been%20arrested%20in%20this%20connection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20leaders%20have%20denied%20the%20allegations%20and%20accused%20the%20BJP-led%20central%20government%20of%20using%20probe%20agencies%20such%20as%20ED%20and%20CBI%20for%20political%20motives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20has%20also%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20BJP%20over%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20arrest%2C%20alleging%20that%20it%20was%20trying%20to%20prevent%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20from%20campaigning%20for%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%20The%20party%2C%20which%20is%20in%20power%20in%20Delhi%2C%20has%20maintained%20that%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20will%20continue%20as%20Chief%20Minister.%20AAP%20ministers%20Atishi%20and%20Saurabh%20Bharadwaj%20have%20said%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20is%20issuing%20orders%20from%20the%20ED's%20lock-up%20and%20assured%20Delhi%20residents%20that%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20is%20constantly%20thinking%20about%20their%20well-being.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711527000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fseblkpqo_arvind-kejriwal_625x300_26_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-enforcement-directorate-delhi-high-court-to-hear-arvind-kejriwals-petition-against-arrest-5318028%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20is%20set%20to%20hear%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20challenge%20to%20his%20arrest%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20last%20week%20and%20a%20trial%20court's%20order%20that%20remanded%20him%20in%20the%20agency's%20custody%20for%20a%20week.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-enforcement-directorate-delhi-high-court-to-hear-arvind-kejriwals-petition-against-arrest-5318028%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20Summons%20US%20Diplomat%20Over%20Comments%20On%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20Arrest%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20on%20Wednesday%20held%20a%2040-minute%20meeting%20United%20States'%20Acting%20Deputy%20Chief%20of%20Mission%2C%20who%20was%20summoned%20to%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs'%20office%20in%20Delhi's%20South%20Block.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDetails%20of%20the%20meeting%20have%20not%20been%20released%2C%20but%20this%20comes%20a%20day%20after%20a%20US%20State%20Department%20spokesperson%20said%20it%20is%20monitoring%20reports%20of%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20arrest%2C%20and%20called%20on%20New%20Delhi%20to%20ensure%20%26quot%3Ba%20fair%20and%20timely%20legal%20process%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20jailed%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20State%20Department's%20comments%20came%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20days%20after%20Germany's%20Foreign%20Office%20stressed%20that%20Mr%20Kejriwal%2C%20like%20any%20other%20Indian%20citizen%20facing%20charges%2C%20is%20entitled%20to%20a%20fair%20and%20impartial%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20government%20reacted%20strongly%20to%20the%20comment%2C%20summoning%20the%20German%20envoy%20and%20labelling%20the%20Foreign%20Office%20spokesperson's%20remark%20%26quot%3Bblatant%20interference%20in%20internal%20matters%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20see%20such%20remarks%20as%20interfering%20in%20our%20judicial%20process%20and%20undermining%20the%20independence%20of%20our%20judiciary%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20External%20Affairs%20Ministry%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BBiased%20assumptions%20are%20most%20unwarranted.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20India's%20protest%20to%20Germany%2C%20the%20State%20Department%20spokesperson%20told%20Reuters%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20refer%20you%20to%20the%20German%20Foreign%20Ministry%20for%20comment%20on%20their%20discussions%20with%20the%20Indian%20government.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArvind%20Kejriwal%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20last%20week%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20alleged%20liquor%20policy%20scam%20that%20has%20roiled%20his%20AAP%20and%20provoked%20furious%20protests%20from%20the%20opposition%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20was%20this%20week%20sent%20to%20jail%20till%20March%2028.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20believes%20the%20now-scrapped%20liquor%20policy%20provided%20an%20impossibly%20high%20profit%20margin%20of%20185%20per%20cent%20for%20retailers%20and%2012%20per%20cent%20for%20wholesalers.%20Of%20the%20latter%2C%20six%20per%20cent%20-%20over%20Rs%20600%20crore%20-%20were%20bribes%20and%20the%20money%20was%20allegedly%20used%20to%20fund%20the%20AAP's%20poll%20campaigns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20is%20in%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20today%20to%20challenge%20his%20arrest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20has%20labelled%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20as%20a%20key%20conspirator%20in%20this%20case%2C%20but%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20and%20party%20colleagues%20arrested%20in%20this%20matter%20-%20ex-Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Manish%20Sisodia%2C%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Sanjay%20Singh%2C%20and%20former%20Health%20Minister%20Satyendar%20Jain%20-%20have%20all%20denied%20the%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20and%20the%20opposition%20have%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20BJP-led%20central%20government%20for%20using%20central%20agencies%2C%20like%20the%20ED%2C%20to%20target%20rivals%20and%20critics%20before%20the%20general%20election.%20The%20AAP%20has%20criticised%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20arrest%20on%20grounds%20it%20was%20timed%20to%20interfere%20with%20his%20plans%20to%20campaign%20for%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20dismissed%20claims%20it%20uses%20central%20agencies%20as%20described%20by%20the%20opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711526760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fh9kt5g28_india-summons-us-official-_625x300_27_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-summons-us-diplomat-over-comments-on-arvind-kejriwals-arrest-5319322%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20government%20on%20Wednesday%20met%20United%20States'%20Acting%20Deputy%20Chief%20of%20Mission%2C%20who%20was%20summoned%20to%20the%20office%20of%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20in%20Delhi's%20South%20Block.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-summons-us-diplomat-over-comments-on-arvind-kejriwals-arrest-5319322%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mahua%20Moitra%20Summoned%20Again%20In%20Foreign%20Exchange%20Violation%20Case%3A%20Sources%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22Trinamool's%20Mahua%20Moitra%20summoned%20again%20by%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20in%20foreign%20exchange%20violation%20case%3A%20Sources%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711526760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F261uj8ag_mahua-moitra_650x400_28_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmahua-moitra-summoned-again-in-foreign-exchange-violation-case-sources-5319450%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mahua%20Moitra%20Summoned%20Again%20In%20Foreign%20Exchange%20Violation%20Case%3A%20Sources%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22