ticleshow%2F108812875.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BHe'll%20Reveal%20Where%20Money%20Of%20So-Called%20Liquor%20Scam%20Is%26quot%3B%3A%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20Wife%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EArvind%20Kejriwal%20will%20make%20a%20big%20revelation%20in%20the%20alleged%20Delhi%20liquor%20policy%20scam%20that%20has%20roiled%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20and%20led%20to%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20arrest%20just%20weeks%20before%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20his%20wife%20Sunita%20Kejriwal%20said%20Wednesday%20morning%2C%20in%20a%20brief%20riposte%20to%20her%20husband's%20critics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMrs%20Kejriwal%20said%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20-%20arrested%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20last%20week%20and%20remanded%20to%20judicial%20custody%20till%20April%209%20-%20would%20reveal%20the%20location%20of%20%26quot%3Bmoney%20from%20the%20so-called%20liquor%20scam%26quot%3B.%20She%20also%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20over%20attacks%20on%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20after%20he%20issued%20directions%20to%20Atishi%20and%20Saurabh%20Bhardwaj%2C%20the%20city's%20Public%20Works%20and%20Health%20Ministers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BArvindji%20told%20me%20that%20in%20the%20past%20two%20years%20they%20(referring%20to%20probe%20agencies%20like%20the%20ED)%20conducted%20250%20raids%20in%20this%20so-called%20liquor%20policy%20case.%20He%20told%20me%20that%20they%20are%20searching%20for%20the%20money%20from%20this%20so-called%20scam...%20but%20so%20far%20they%20have%20not%20recovered%20a%20single%20paise%20of%20illegal%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20raided%20(ex-Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Manish)%20Sisodia...%20they%20raided%20(Rajya%20Sabha%20MP)%20Sanjay%20Singh...%20they%20raided%20(former%20Health%20Minister%20Satyendar)%20Jain.%20But%20they%20did%20not%20find%20even%20one%20paise.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sisodia%20and%20Mr%20Singh%20were%20both%20arrested%20last%20year%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20alleged%20liquor%20policy%20scam%3B%20the%20former%20has%20been%20in%20jail%20since%20February%20and%20the%20latter%20since%20October.%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20was%20taken%20into%20custody%20in%20dramatic%20circumstances%20last%20week%20after%20a%20Delhi%20court%20refused%20protection%20from%20arrest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister's%20arrest%20triggered%20furious%20protests%20across%20the%20city.%20Opposition%20parties%2C%20including%20the%20Congress%20and%20Bengal's%20ruling%20Trinamool%2C%20have%20spoken%20out%20in%20support%20of%20the%20AAP%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20raided%20us%20(Mr%20Kejriwal's%20home)%20also%20and%20found%20only%20Rs%2073%2C000.%20So%20where%20is%20all%20this%20money%20from%20the%20so-called%20liquor%20scam%3F%20Arvindji%20has%20said%20he%20will%20reveal%20everything%20in%20court%20(tomorrow).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20whole%20country%20will%20bear%20witness.%20He%20said%20he%20has%20proof%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20her%20husband%20had%20given%20her%20a%20message%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Delhi.%20%26quot%3BHe%20said%2C%20'My%20body%20is%20in%20jail...%20but%20my%20spirit%20is%20with%20you'.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20slammed%20BJP%20leaders%20over%20criticism%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister's%20orders%20from%20jail%3B%20on%20Monday%20he%20had%20directed%20Ms%20Atishi%20to%20solve%20water%20supply%20and%20sewerage%20issues%20in%20parts%20of%20the%20city%20and%2C%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20ordered%20Mr%20Bhardwaj%20to%20ensure%20a%20supply%20of%20free%20medicines%20at%20Delhi%20government%20clinics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20orders%20have%20been%20red-flagged%20by%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20claimed%20they%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Bscripted%26quot%3B%20to%20generate%20sympathy%20for%20the%20jailed%20Arvind%20Kejriwal.%20Senior%20BJP%20leader%20Manjinder%20Singh%20Sirsa%20said%20Tuesday%20he%20had%20filed%20a%20complaint%20with%20the%20ED%20and%20Delhi%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20VK%20Saxena%20over%20the%20%26quot%3Bfabricated%26quot%3B%20orders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20totally%20illegal%20and%20unconstitutional...%20and%20a%20criminal%20conspiracy%20against%20the%20people%20of%20Delhi%20and%20the%20office%20of%20the%20Chief%20Minister.%20Kejriwalji%20is%20in%20ED%20custody%20and%20lacks%20the%20legal%20capacity%20to%20issue%20such%20directives%20without%20court%20permission%2C%20which%20has%20not%20been%20granted%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20went%20to%20meet%20Arvindji%20in%20jail%20yesterday%20evening.%20He%20has%20diabetes...%20sugar%20level%20is%20an%20issue.%20But%20he%20remains%20determined.%20Two%20days%20earlier%20he%20sent%20an%20order%20to%20Atishiji.%20Tell%20me%20what%20wrong%20he%20did...%20should%20he%20not%20be%20aware%20of%20people's%20problems%3F%20But%20now%20the%20centre%20has%20attacked%20your%20Chief%20Minister.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDoes%20the%20centre%20want%20to%20destroy%20Delhi%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Fchannel%2F0029Va4lixw7z4kcvZI9JM12%5C%22%3EClick%20on%20the%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20all%20the%20latest%20updates%20from%20NDTV%20on%20your%20chat.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711524600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F3bto3a94_sunita-kejriwal-_625x300_27_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhell-reveal-in-court-where-money-is-arvind-kejriwal-wifes-big-claim-5319025%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Arvind%20Kejriwal%20will%20make%20a%20big%20revelation%20in%20the%20alleged%20Delhi%20liquor%20policy%20scam%20that%20has%20roiled%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20and%20led%20to%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20arrest%20just%20weeks%20before%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elect