he%20Medinipur%20seat%2C%20which%20he%20currently%20represents%2C%20to%20Bardhaman%20Durgapur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20comments%20left%20the%20BJP%20red-faced%20and%20provided%20fodder%20to%20the%20Opposition%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20BJP%20was%20trying%20to%20corner%20the%20Congress%20over%20offensive%20social%20media%20posts%20from%20the%20profile%20of%20its%20spokesperson%20Supriya%20Shrinate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Shrinate%20has%20said%20the%20derogatory%20posts%20on%20BJP%20candidate%20and%20actor%20Kangana%20Ranaut%20were%20made%20without%20her%20knowledge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHours%20after%20Trinamool%20launched%20an%20attack%20on%20the%20BJP%20over%20Mr%20Ghosh's%20remarks%2C%20the%20party%20leadership%20demanded%20an%20explanation%20from%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Ghosh%20has%20said%20he%20will%20respond%20to%20the%20party's%20questions.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20a%20controversy%20has%20erupted%20over%20my%20remarks.%20I%20have%20no%20personal%20enmity%20with%20the%20Chief%20Minister.%20I%20have%20only%20questioned%20the%20political%20remarks%20she%20has%20made%20to%20mislead%20people.%20A%20lot%20of%20people%20have%20problems%20with%20my%20language%20and%20usage%20of%20words.%20My%20party%20has%20also%20pointed%20it%20out.%20Many%20have%20said%20it%20is%20unparliamentary.%20If%20that%20is%20the%20case%2C%20I%20regret%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20I%20have%20a%20question.%20A%20leader%20from%20her%20party%2C%20her%20family%2C%20has%20said%20worse%20things%20about%20the%20leader%20of%20BJP's%20legislative%20party%20(Suvendu%20Adhikari)%20and%20his%20father.%20Don't%20they%20have%20any%20respect%3F%20His%20father%20is%20a%20senior%20politician%20in%20Bengal.%20The%20Trinamool%20did%20not%20protest%20then.%20Why%20didn't%20they%20issue%20a%20statement%3F%20I%20have%20made%20a%20political%20statement%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20without%20naming%20Abhishek%20Banerjee%2C%20Trinamool's%20national%20ge