ornia%20has%20released%20new%20documents%20accusing%C2%A0Mark%20Zuckerberg-led%20Meta%20Platforms%20of%20snooping%20on%C2%A0Snapchat%2C%20YouTube%20and%20Amazon%20users.%20According%20to%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftechcrunch.com%2F2024%2F03%2F26%2Ffacebook-secret-project-snooped-snapchat-user-traffic%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ETechCrunch%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0Facebook%20launched%20a%20secret%20initiative%20called%20'Project%20Ghostbusters'%20in%202016%20to%20intercept%20and%20decrypt%20the%20network%20traffic%20between%20people%20using%20Snapchat's%20app%20and%20its%20servers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20initiative%20was%20designed%20to%20understand%20user%20behaviour%20and%20gain%20a%20competitive%20advantage%20over%20Snapchat%2C%20as%20per%20the%20court%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20document%20also%20includes%20internal%20Facebook%20emails%20discussing%20the%20project.%20In%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.courtlistener.com%2Frecap%2Fgov.uscourts.cand.369872%2Fgov.uscourts.cand.369872.735.0.pdf%5C%22%3Einternal%20email%20dated%20June%209%2C%202016%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Facebook%20CEO%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%20emphasised%20the%20need%20to%20obtain%20analytics%20on%20Snapchat%20despite%20its%20encrypted%20traffic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20wrote%2C%20''Whenever%20someone%20asks%20a%20question%20about%20Snapchat%2C%20the%20answer%20is%20usually%20that%20because%20their%20traffic%20is%20encrypted%20we%20have%20no%20analytics%20about%20them.%20Given%20how%20quickly%20they're%20growing%2C%20it%20seems%20important%20to%20figure%20out%20a%20new%20way%20to%20get%20reliable%20analytics%20about%20them.%20Perhaps%20we%20need%20to%20do%20panels%20or%20write%20custom%20software.%20You%20should%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20do%20this.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFacebook%20engineers%20then%20proposed%20using%20Onavo%2C%20a%20service%20similar%20to%20a%20Virtual%20Private%20Network%20acquired%20by%20Facebook%20in%202013%2C%20to%20intercept%20specific%20subdomains'%20traffic.%20A%20month%20later%2C%20they%20presented%20proposal%20kits%20that%20could%20be%20installed%20on%20iOS%20and%20Android%20platforms.%20These%20kits%20would%20intercept%20traffic%20for%20particular%20subdomains%2C%20enabling%20the%20team%20to%20analyze%20in-app%20usage%20by%20reading%20what%20would%20typically%20be%20encrypted%20traffic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20project%20was%20later%20expanded%20to%20include%20Amazon%20and%20YouTube.%20A%20team%20of%20senior%20executives%20and%20roughly%2041%20lawyers%20worked%20on%20Project%20Ghostbusters%2C%20according%20to%20court%20filings.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''We%20now%20can%20measure%20detailed%20in-app%20activity%20from%20''parsing%20Snapchat%20analytics%20collected%20from%20incentivized%20participants%20in%20Onavo's%20research%20program%2C''%20read%20another%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20not%20all%20Facebook%20employees%20were%C2%A0in%20favour%20of%20Project%20Ghostbusters.%C2%A0Some%20employees%2C%20including%20Jay%20Parikh%2C%20Facebook's%20then-head%20of%20infrastructure%20engineering%2C%20and%20Pedro%20Canahuati%2C%20the%20then-head%20of%20security%20engineering%2C%20expressed%20their%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''I%20can't%20think%20of%20a%20good%20argument%20for%20why%20this%20is%20okay.%20No%20security%20person%20is%20ever%20comfortable%20with%20this%2C%20no%20matter%20what%20consent%20we%20get%20from%20the%20general%20public.%20The%20general%20public%20just%20doesn't%20know%20how%20this%20stuff%20works%2C''%20Mr%20Canahuati%20wrote%20in%20an%20email%2C%20included%20in%20the%20court%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFacebook%20shut%20down%20Onavo%20in%202019%20after%20an%20investigation%20revealed%20that%20Facebook%20had%20been%20secretly%20paying%20teenagers%20to%20use%20Onavo%20so%20the%20company%20could%20access%20all%20of%20their%20web%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711518660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-01%2F21mqmg78_mark-zuckerberg-getty_625x300_30_January_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fnew-documents-reveal-facebook-snooped-on-users-snapchat-youtube-traffic-in-secret-project-5318542%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Facebook%20launched%20a%20secret%20initiative%20called%20'Project%20Ghostbusters'%20in%202016%20to%20intercept%20and%20decrypt%20the%20network%20traffic%20between%20Snapchat's%20app%20and%20its%20servers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fnew-documents-reveal-facebook-snooped-on-users-snapchat-youtube-traffic-in-secret-project-5318542%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Time%20Up%20For%20Shaheen%20Afridi%3F%20Babar%20Azam%20Asked%20To%20Take%20Pak%20Captaincy%20Again%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20it%20appears%20has%20lost%20faith%20in%20the%20ability%20of%20Shan%20Masood%20and%20Shaheen%20Shah%20Afridi%20to%20lead%20the%20national%20side%20and%20feels%20former%20skipper%20Babar%20Azam%20is%20the%20best%20choice%20to%20captain%20the%20side%20once%20again.%20Babar%20had%20quit%20as%20Pakistan%20captain%20across%20all%20formats%20after%20his%20team%20failed%20to%20make%20it%20past%20the%20group%20stages%20during%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20in%20India%20last%20year.%20While%20Masood%20was%20appointed%20captain%20in%20the%20Test%20format%2C%20Shaheen%20was%20made%20the%20T20I%20skipper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20in%20the%20PCB%20think-tank%20said%20the%20board%20had%20come%20to%20the%20conclusion%20that%2C%20with%20no%20viable%20option%20available%2C%20Babar%20was%20the%20best%20choice%20to%20lead%20the%20side%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20funny%20part%20is%20that%20the%20powers%20that%20be%20appear%20to%20have%20lost%20faith%20in%20Shan%20Masood%20and%20Shaheen%20Shah%20Afridi's%20ability%20to%20lead%20the%2