e%20Pavan%20Davuluri%20To%20Head%20Microsoft%20Windows%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPavan%20Davuluri%2C%20an%20IIT%20Madras%20alumni%2C%20was%20appointed%20the%20new%20head%20of%20Microsoft%20Windows%20and%20Surface%2C%20making%20him%20the%20latest%20Indian%20to%20take%20on%20a%20leadership%20role%20at%20a%20Big%20Tech%20company%20much%20like%20Google's%20Sundar%20Pichai%20and%20Microsoft's%20Satya%20Nadella.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Davuluri%20takes%20over%20from%20longtime%20product%20chief%20Panos%20Panay%20who%20left%20the%20department%20to%20join%20Amazon%20last%20year.%20Earlier%2C%20Mr%20Davuluri%20oversaw%20the%20Surface%20group%20while%20Mikhail%20Parakhin%20headed%20the%20Windows%20department.%20After%20Mr%20Parakhin%20and%20Mr%20Panay%20quit%2C%20he%20has%20taken%20over%20both%20Windows%20and%20Surface%20departments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20internal%20memo%20from%20Rajesh%20Jha%2C%20Microsoft's%20head%20of%20experiences%20and%20devices%2C%20accessed%20by%20The%20Verge%20outlined%20the%20new%20hierarchy%20in%20the%20organisation.%20He%20said%20the%20decision%20will%20help%20the%20organisation%20to%20take%20a%20%26quot%3Bholistic%20approach%26quot%3B%20to%20build%20its%20devices%20and%20experiences%20in%20the%20%26quot%3BAI%20era%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20part%20of%20this%20change%2C%20we%20are%20bringing%20together%20the%20Windows%20Experiences%20and%20Windows%20%2B%20Devices%20teams%20as%20a%20core%20part%20of%20the%20Experiences%20%2B%20Devices%20(E%2BD)%20division.%20This%20will%20enable%20us%20to%20take%20a%20holistic%20approach%20to%20building%20silicon%2C%20systems%2C%20experiences%2C%20and%20devices%20that%20span%20Windows%20client%20and%20cloud%20for%20this%20AI%20era.%20Pavan%20Davuluri%20will%20lead%20this%20team%20and%20continue%20to%20report%20to%20me.%20Shilpa%20Ranganathan%20and%20Jeff%20Johnson%20and%20their%20teams%20will%20report%20directly%20to%20Pavan.%20The%20Windows%20team%20will%20continue%20to%20work%20closely%20with%20the%20Microsoft%20AI%20team%20on%20AI%2C%20silicon%2C%20and%20experiences%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Davuluri%20has%20worked%20for%20over%2023%20years%20at%20Microsoft%20and%20was%20involved%20in%20its%20work%20with%20Qualcomm%20and%20AMD%20to%20create%20processors%20for%20Surface.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20excited%20for%20this%20team%20to%20help%20Microsoft%20AI%20achieve%20its%20bold%20ambition%20to%20build%20world-class%20consumer%20AI%20products.%20And%20I%20very%20much%20look%20forward%20to%20closely%20partnering%20with%20Mustafa%20and%20the%20team%20as%20we%20bring%20our%20AI%20products%2C%20including%20Copilot%2C%20to%20the%20breadth%20of%20our%20E%2BD%20products%20and%20services%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20memo%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reorganisation%20announcement%20comes%20days%20after%20Google%20DeepMind%20co-founder%20and%20former%20Inflection%20AI%20CEO%20Mustafa%20Suleyman%20joined%20Microsoft%20as%20the%20CEO%20of%20its%20new%20AI%20team.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711515420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fm4itojuo_pavan-davuluri_625x300_27_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fiit-madras-graduate-pavan-davuluri-to-head-microsoft-windows-5318388%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pavan%20Davuluri%2C%20an%20IIT%20Madras%20alumni%2C%20was%20appointed%20the%20new%20head%20of%20Microsoft%20Windows%20and%20Surface%2C%20making%20him%20the%20latest%20Indian%20to%20take%20on%20a%20leadership%20role%20at%20a%20Big%20Tech%20company%20much%20like%20Google's%20Sundar%20Pichai%20and%20Microsoft's%20Satya%20Nadella.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fiit-madras-graduate-pavan-davuluri-to-head-microsoft-windows-5318388%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Historic%20defense%20shift%3A%20Why%20pacifist%20Japan%20plans%20t