C%20she%20calls%20herself%20the%20daughter%20of%20Goa.%20When%20she%20goes%20to%20Tripura%2C%20she%20says%20that%20she%20is%20the%20daughter%20of%20Tripura.%20She%20should%20first%20identify%20her%20own%20father...%26quot%3B%20Dilip%20Ghosh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMamata%20Banerjee-led%20Trinamool%20Congress%20filed%20a%20complaint%20with%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20against%20Mr%20Ghosh%20for%20his%20remarks%20on%20Ms%20Banerjee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20TMC%20said%20that%20the%20BJP%20leader%20has%20violated%20the%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%20by%20making%20personal%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiting%20the%20clause%20under%20the%20poll%20code%2C%20which%20states%20that%20%26quot%3Bno%20political%20party%20or%20candidate%20should%20indulge%20in%20any%20activities%20or%20make%20any%20statements%20that%20would%20amount%20to%20an%20attack%20on%20the%20personal%20life%20of%20any%20person%20or%20statements%20that%20may%20be%20malicious%20or%20offend%20decency%20and%20morality%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20ruling%20party%20in%20West%20Bengal%20urged%20the%20Election%20Commission%20to%20immediately%20take%20action%20against%20Mr%20Ghosh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMr%20Ghosh's%20comments%20not%20only%20cross%20the%20boundaries%20of%20decency%20but%20also%20perpetuate%20a%20culture%20of%20misogyny%20and%20disrespect%20towards%20women%20in%20positions%20of%20power%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20letter%20to%20the%20poll%20body%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20remarks%20by%20the%20BJP%20leader%20have%20drawn%20sharp%20criticism%20from%20the%20TMC%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSuch%20mentality%20of%20BJP%20leaders%20humiliates%20Nari%20Shakti.%20He%20earlier%20made%20derogatory%20remarks%20against%20Maa%20Durga.%20He%20should%20be%20arrested%20under%20the%20POCSO%20Act%20for%20what%20he%20said%20about%20Mamata%20Banerjee...%26quot%3B%20TMC%20leader%20Kirti%20Azad%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWest%20Bengal%20Minister%20Shashi%20Panja%20said%20that%20the%20BJP%20leader%20is%20such%20a%20petty%20man%20and%20such%20people%20should%20be%20defeated%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20all%20the%20daughters%20of%20India.%20Wherever%20we%20go%2C%20we%20will%20be%20the%20daughters%20of%20India.%20Whichever%20state%20we%20visit%2C%20we%20will%20be%20its%20daughters.%20Dilip%20Ghosh%20is%20such%20a%20petty%20man.%20He%20is%20contesting%20elections%20and%20he%20thinks%20that%20he%20will%20win%20and%20become%20a%20public%20representative.%20Will%20such%20a%20man%20be%20the%20public%20representative%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20BJP's%20DNA%20and%20its%20character%20are%20so%20bad%20that%20they%20are%20attacking%20women%20and%20Mamata%20Didi.%20They%20want%20to%20suppress%20and%20weaken%20women%20if%20they%20grow%20powerful.%20If%20this%20is%20the%20mindset%20of%20politicians%2C%20what%20will%20be%20the%20mindset%20of%20workers%3F%20What%20impact%20will%20it%20have%20on%20the%20ground%20level%3F%20If%20you%20insult%20women%2C%20atrocities%20against%20them%20will%20increase.%20Such%20people%20should%20be%20defeated.%20The%20Election%20Commission%20should%20take%20action.%20They%20are%20so%20greedy%20for%20power%20that%20they%20can%20stoop%20to%20any%20level.%20It%20is%20their%20frustration%20that%20is%20in%20action%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711508940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fr8unv5s_dilip-ghosh_625x300_27_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findecent-bjp-chief-jp-nadda-seeks-dilip-ghoshs-clarification-for-his-remarks-on-mamata-banerjee-5317924%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22BJP%20president%20JP%20Nadda%20on%20Tuesday%20issued%20a%20notice%20seeking%20clarification%20fro