ernal%20medicine%20while%20his%20brother%20is%20an%20IIT-Delhi%20alumnus.%20The%20doctor%20said%20he%20and%20his%20brother%20followed%20the%20same%20kind%20of%20gruelling%20schedule%20for%20three%20years%20and%20got%20admission%20into%20one%20of%20the%20best%20government%20medical%20colleges.%20Meanwhile%2C%20his%20brother%20also%20got%20a%20good%20branch%20at%20IIT%20Delhi%20and%20is%20now%20settled%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''Me%20and%20my%20brother%20almost%20followed%20the%20same%20routine%20for%203%20years%2C%20I%20got%20one%20of%20the%20best%20govt%20medical%20colleges%20and%20he%20got%20a%20good%20branch%20%40%20IIT%20Delhi%2C%20now%20settled%20in%20the%20US.%20Telling%20you%20there%20is%20no%20shortcut%2C''%20Dr%20Shraddhey%20Katiyar%20wrote%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESee%20the%20tweet%20here%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EMe%20and%20my%20brother%20almost%20followed%20the%20same%20routine%20for%203%20years%20%2C%20I%20got%20one%20of%20the%20best%20govt%20medical%20college%20and%20he%20got%20a%20good%20branch%20%40%20IIT%20Delhi%2C%20now%20settled%20in%20US%20.%20Telling%20you%20there%20is%20no%20shortcut%20.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F2a8n65P2hL%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F2a8n65P2hL%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Dr%20SHRADDHEY%20KATIYAR%20(%40Wegiveyouhealt1)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FWegiveyouhealt1%2Fstatus%2F1770668753682096405%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2021%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20users%20agreed%20with%20his%20tweet%2C%20saying%20that%20aspirants%20who%20come%20from%20humble%20backgrounds%20have%20no%20option%2C%20but%20to%20put%20in%20the%20hours.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20user%20said%2C%20''Absolutely%20no%20shortcut.%20I%20have%20still%20kept%20my%20schedule%20of%20study%20for%206%20months%20