hat-does-it-mean-for-your-cargo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egeneral%20average%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20dictates%20that%20companies%20with%20even%20a%20single%20container%20aboard%20a%20ship%20have%20to%20split%20the%20damages%20pro%20rata%20based%20on%20the%20number%20of%20containers%2C%20ensuring%20all%20the%20stakeholders%20benefiting%20from%20the%20voyage%20are%20splitting%20the%20risk%2C%20Petersen%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Drone%20footage%20shows%20aftermath%20of%20the%20Dali%20container%20ship's%20collision%20into%20the%20Francis%20Scott%20Key%20Bridge%20in%20Baltimore%2C%20Maryland%2C%20on%20March%2026%2C%202024.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660324a51caec1275a69b212%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221152%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDrone%20footage%20shows%20aftermath%20of%20the%20Dali%20container%20ship's%20collision%20into%20the%20Francis%20Scott%20Key%20Bridge%20in%20Baltimore%2C%20Maryland%2C%20on%20March%2026%2C%202024.%3Cp%3EAnadolu%20Agency%20via%20Reuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20principle%20dates%20back%20hundreds%20of%20years%20and%20was%20originally%20meant%20to%20ensure%20sailors%20on%20board%20a%20ship%20weren't%20worried%20about%20specific%20cargo%20if%20a%20disaster%20required%20them%20to%20start%20throwing%20containers%20overboard%2C%20according%20to%20Petersen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20will%20pay%20for%20everything%20else%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20majority%20of%20the%20financial%20fallout%20is%20likely%20to%20lay%20primarily%20with%20the%20insurance%20industry%2C%20according%20to%20media%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndustry%20experts%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F17cf3f2e-e64d-4666-b1c2-2723347c2ada%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFT%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20insurers%20could%20pay%20out%20losses%20for%20bridge%20damage%2C%20port%20disruption%2C%20and%20any%20loss%20of%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20collapse%20could%20drive%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20largest%20claims%20ever%20to%20hit%20the%20marine%20(re)insurance%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20John%20Miklus%2C%20president%20of%20the%20American%20Institute%20of%20Marine%20Underwriters%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insurancebusinessmag.com%2Fus%2Fnews%2Fmarine%2Fmajor-reinsurers-and-pandi-club-on-hook-for-baltimore-bridge-disaster-482812.aspx%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInsurance%20Business.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20the%20outlet%20that%20the%20loss%20of%20revenue%20from%20tolls%20while%20the%20bridge%20is%20being%20rebuilt%20will%20be%20expensive%2C%20as%20will%20any%20liability%20claims%20from%20deaths%20or%20injuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Dali%20is%20covered%20by%20the%20Britannia%20Steam%20Ship%20Insurance%20Association%20Ltd.%2C%20known%20as%20Britannia%20P%26amp%3BI%20Club%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.spglobal.com%2Fmarketintelligence%2Fen%2Fnews-insights%2Flatest-news-headlines%2Freinsurers-marine-market-to-bear-brunt-of-baltimore-bridge-collapse-80988297%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ES%26amp%3BP%20Global%20Market%20Intelligence.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBritannia%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider%20but%20told%20FT%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bworking%20closely%20with%20the%20ship%20manager%20and%20relevant%20authorities%20to%20establish%20the%20facts%20and%20to%20help%20ensure%20that%20this%20situation%20is%20dealt%20with%20quickly%20and%20professionally.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBritannia%20is%20one%20of%2012%20mutual%20insurers%20included%20in%20the%20International%20Group%20of%20P%26amp%3BI%20Clubs%2C%20which%20maintains%20more%20than%20%243%20billion%20of%20reinsurance%20cover%2C%20sources%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter%20told%20Insurance%20Business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBritannia%20itself%20is%20liable%20for%20the%20fi