Fa%3E%C2%A0(PMJJBY).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDays%20after%20his%20account%20was%20debited%20on%2029%20December%202022%2C%20upset%20that%20the%20bank%2C%20supposed%20to%20safeguard%20his%20money%2C%20took%20it%20without%20permission%2C%20Kumar%2C%2026%2C%20sought%20a%20copy%20of%20his%20insurance%20application%20form%20from%20the%20bank%20under%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcic.gov.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FRTI-Act_English.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERight%20to%20Information%20(RTI)%20Act%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%202005.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%202%20February%202023%2C%20his%20bank%2C%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20(SBI)%2C%20replied%2C%20%E2%80%9CApplication%20form%20not%20found%20for%20the%20aforesaid%20insurance.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bank%20has%20not%20granted%20him%20a%20refund%20for%20this%20unsolicited%20insurance.%20He%20told%3Cb%3E%C2%A0Article%2014%3C%2Fb%3E%C2%A0in%20an%20interview%20that%20he%20was%20still%20looking%20for%20a%20way%20%E2%80%9Cto%20get%20out%20of%20this%20dirty%20system%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20him%2C%20many%20across%20the%20country%20have%20protested%20unauthorised%20debits%20from%20their%20bank%20accounts%20for%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20insurance%20schemes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20life%20insurance%2C%20banks%20have%20also%20been%20enrolling%20customers%20without%20consent%20in%20the%20accident%20insurance%20scheme%2C%20called%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjansuraksha.gov.in%2FFiles%2FPMSBY%2FENGLISH%2FRules.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPradhan%20Mantri%20Suraksha%20Bima%20Yojana%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0(PMSBY).%20These%20complaints%20also%20extend%20to%20the%20centre%E2%80%99s%20micro-pension%20scheme%2C%20called%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnpscra.nsdl.co.in%2Fnsdl%2Fscheme-details%2FOct162015.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAtal%20Pension%20Yojana%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0(APY).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20Kumar%20got%20enrolled%20in%20PMJJBY%20without%20consent%2C%20his%20mother%20was%20enrolled%20in%20the%20APY%20without%20consent%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20PMJJBY%20premium%20is%20Rs%20436%20a%20year%2C%20PMSBY%20costs%20Rs%2020%20a%20year.%20Once%20a%20customer%20is%20subscribed%20to%20these%20schemes%2C%20the%20fees%20are%20deducted%20automatically%20from%20his%2Fher%20account%20annually.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PMJJBY%20provides%20a%20cover%20of%20Rs%20200%2C000%20to%20a%20policyholder%E2%80%99s%20nominee%20in%20the%20event%20of%20death%20due%20to%20any%20reason.%20The%20PMSBY%20provides%20Rs%20200%2C000%20in%20case%20of%20death%20due%20to%20an%20accident%20and%20Rs%20100%2C000%20in%20case%20of%20a%20severe%20accident%20injury.%20The%20APY%20offers%20a%20monthly%20pension%20of%20up%20to%20Rs%205%2C000%20after%20the%20age%20of%2060.%20The%20monthly%20fee%20depends%20on%20the%20pension%20plan%20selected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOften%2C%20those%20enrolled%20in%20insurance%20schemes%20without%20consent%20are%20not%20aware%20that%20they%20are%20paying%20a%20premium%20for%20an%20insurance%20cover.%20This%20prevents%20family%20members%20from%20availing%20the%20schemes%E2%80%99%20benefits%2C%20rendering%20their%20premium%20payments%E2%80%94unauthorised%20to%20begin%20with%E2%80%94futile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolicy%20certificates%20of%20such%20customers%2C%20accessed%20by%20this%20reporter%2C%20showed%20bogus%20nominees.%20This%20also%20restricts%20policyholders%E2%80%99%20families%20from%20availing%20the%20benefits%20of%20the%20schemes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20launched%20these%20low-cost%20welfare%20schemes%20in%20May%202015%20to%20provide%20financial%20security%20to%20the%20poor.%20From%20the%20beginning%2C%C2%A0%20banks%20faced%20allegations%20of%20enrolling%20customers%20in%20these%20schemes%20through%20fraudulent%20practices%20(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsushilmaheshwar%2Fstatus%2F606999850983366657%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.complaintboard.in%2Fcomplaints-reviews%2Ficici-l414630.html%23c1795625%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Farticle%2Fsbi-kerala-making-customers-join-pms-suraksha-bima-yojana-without-permission-30317%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E)%2C%20purportedly%20because%20of%20government%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20previous%20reports%20for%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farticle-14.com%2Fpost%2Fhow-an-aadhaar-fraud-forces-the-poor-into-paying-for-welfare-schemes-they-do-not-want-63f57eb9e8d15%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cb%3EArticle%2014%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbanking%2Fbanks-have-been-charging-customers-for-government-insurance-they-never-wanted%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20this%20reporter%20has%20described%20various%20ploys%20through%20which%20banks%E2%80%99%20branches%20and%20field%20staff%20force%20these%20schemes%20upon%20their%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENew%20evidence%20reveals%20that%20this%20malpractice%20has%20since%20been%20institutionalised%2C%20with%20regional%2C%20zonal%20and%20even%20head%20offices%20executing%20these%20frauds%20and%20forcing%20branches%20to%20conceal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EHuge%20Targets%2C%20Quick%20Fixes%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20quickest%20albeit%20illegal%20way%20to%20enrol%20a%20high%20number%20of%20customers%20appears%20to%20be%20what%20is%20called%20%E2%80%9Cbulk%20activation%E2%80%9D%2C%20where%20banks%20can%20upload%20and%20approve%20many%20customers%E2%80%99%20details%20into%20the%20insurance-activation%20portal%20all%20at%20once%20using%20a%20spreadsheet%20or%20another%20bulk%20upload%20file.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20matter%20how%20steep%20the%20targets%2C%20they%20can%20be%20met%20with%20just%20a%20few%20clicks%20as%20long%20as%20the%20bank%20does%20not%20mind%20enrolling%20customers%20without%20their%20knowledge.%20Bank%20employees%E2%80%99%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Falashshukla%2Fstatus%2F1744036406429733166%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eposts%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0on%20X%20illustrate%20that%20this%20mode%20of%20enrolling%20customers%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20fact%20at%20banks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20August%202023%2C%20an%20officers%E2%80%99%20union%20of%20government-run%20UCO%20Bank%20sent%20a%20letter%20to%20its%20managing%20director%20%26amp%3B%20CEO%2C%20alleging%20that%20account%20holders%20in%20Dehradun%20were%20illegally%20enrolled%20in%20these%20government%20schemes%20from%20the%20back-end%20by%20the%20head%20office.%C2%A0%3Cb%3EArticle%2014%3C%2Fb%3E%C2%A0has%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20says%20that%20in%20July-end%2C%20the%20zonal%20office%20in%20Dehradun%20sent%20the%20branches%20a%20list%20of%20accounts%20eligible%20for%20PMJJBY%20and%20PMSBY%20and%20asked%20the%20branches%20to%20activate%20the%20schemes%20in%20all%20of%20them%2C%20the%20letter%20said.%20Many%20branch%20managers%20refused%20to%20do%20so%20without%20customers%E2%80%99%20consent%2C%20only%20for%20the%20head%20office%20to%20do%20this%20from%20the%20back-end.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20union%E2%80%99s%20letter%20said%20customer%20complaints%20began%20to%20trickle%20in%2C%20and%20branch%20managers%20requested%20their%20zonal%20office%20to%20issue%20refunds%2C%20but%20the%20zonal%20office%20instead%20instructed%20them%20to%20collect%20and%20backdate%20enrolment%20forms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20employee%20of%20government-owned%20Canara%20Bank%20told%20this%20reporter%20that%20a%20similar%20story%20unfolded%20in%20Rajasthan%20last%20June.%20He%20said%20that%20regional%20offices%20sent%20branches%20lists%20of%20their%20customers%20eligible%20for%20PMJJBY.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20employee%20shared%20screenshots%20of%20the%20bank%E2%80%99s%20content%20management%20system%2C%20showing%20that%20PMJJBY%20was%20activated%20on%20customers%E2%80%99%20accounts%20in%20bulk%20by%20an%20assistant%20general%20manager%20posted%20in%20a%20regional%20office.%C2%A0%3Cb%3EArticle%2014%3C%2Fb%3E%C2%A0has%20sent%20queries%20by%20email%20to%20this%20officer%20and%20is%20awaiting%20a%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20reporter%E2%80%99s%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbanking%2Fbanks-have-been-charging-customers-for-government-insurance-they-never-wanted%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprevious%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0on%20illegal%20enrolment%20of%20customers%20in%20these%20schemes%20was%20based%20on%20similar%20evidence%20of%20bulk%20activation%20in%20Canara%20Bank%E2%80%99s%20West%20Bengal%20unit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20SBI%20employee%20from%20the%20bank%E2%80%99s%20Delhi%20circle%20shared%20with%C2%A0%3Cb%3EArticle%2014%3C%2Fb%3E%C2%A0screenshots%20of%20the%20bank%E2%80%99s%20de%20facto%20official%20WhatsApp%20group%20in%20October%202023.%20(Banks%20do%20not%20recognise%20WhatsApp%20as%20an%20official%20mode%20of%20communication%2C%20but%20liaisoning%20between%20regional%2Fzonal%20offices%20and%20branches%20does%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthekanal.in%2Fen-IN%2Fdetails%2F65437f7df146df001331d97c%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etake%20place%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0on%20WhatsApp%20groups.)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20WhatsApp%20screenshots%20sent%20by%20the%20SBI%20employee%20showed%20bank%20employees%20being%20given%20instructions%20on%20how%20to%20initiate%20bulk%20enrolment%20of%20customers%20in%20PMSBY.%20This%20employee%20also%20shared%20screenshots%20of%20the%20bulk%20upload%20files.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Gujarat%20resident%20told%20this%20reporter%20that%20his%20wife%E2%80%99s%20SBI%20account%20was%20auto-debited%20for%20PMJJBY%20on%2019%20January%202024.%20He%20said%20that%20when%20she%20went%20to%20her%20branch%20to%20seek%20an%20explanation%2C%20the%20branch%20told%20her%20that%20many%20accounts%20were%20debited%20because%20of%20a%20technical%20error%2C%20and%20now%20the%20bank%20was%20offering%20a%20full%20refund.%20To%20refund%20the%20money%2C%20the%20bank%20asked%20her%20to%20fill%20a%20form.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F26162036%2FUntitled.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22762%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F26162036%2FUntitled.jpeg%20762w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F26162036%2FUntitled-300x256.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-703267%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22650%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAt%20this%20SBI%20branch%2C%20customers%20who%20questioned%20unauthorised%20debits%20for%20insurance%20were%20readily%20handed%20a%20refund%20form.%20Photo%20courtesy%20Article%2014%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20customer%E2%80%99s%20husband%20told%20this%20reporter%20that%20he%20spoke%20with%20the%20branch%20manager%2C%20who%20apologetically%20said%20that%20he%20had%20received%20a%20list%20of%20accounts%20from%20his%20regional%20office%20and%20had%20no%20option%20but%20to%20debit%20them%20to%20save%20his%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESBI%20is%20India%E2%80%99s%20largest%20public%20sector%20bank.%20The%20second%20largest%20government%20bank%2C%20Bank%20of%20Baroda%2C%20also%20uses%20bulk%20activation%20to%20meet%20enrolment%20targets%20without%20customers%E2%80%99%20consent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20Bank%20of%20Baroda%20employee%20from%20Karnataka%20shared%20screenshots%20of%20emails%20from%20December%202022%20and%20February%202023%2C%20bearing%20details%20of%20eligible%20customers%20and%20instructing%20branches%20to%20enrol%20them%20in%20PMJJBY%20and%20PMSBY%20via%20bulk%20activation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F26162126%2FUntitled-1.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F26162126%2FUntitled-1.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F26162126%2FUntitled-1-300x170.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F26162126%2FUntitled-1-1024x579.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-703268%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22678%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EUsually%2C%20banks%20go%20about%20illegal%20enrolment%20discreetly%2C%20through%20WhatsApp%20groups.%20But%20this%20regional%20office%20of%20Bank%20of%20Baroda%20had%20no%20qualms%20sending%20bulk%20upload%20files%20via%20the%20official%20mail.%20Photo%20courtesy%20Article%2014%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20employee%20said%20he%20had%20to%20do%20bulk%20enrolment%20of%20customers%20in%20PMSBY%20without%20their%20consent%20when%20his%20deputy%20regional%20manager%20asked%20him%20to%20do%20so%20and%20provided%20him%20with%20the%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%C2%A0%3Cb%3EArticle%2014%3C%2Fb%3E%E2%80%99s%20queries%20about%20enrolling%20customers%20without%20their%20consent%2C%20UCO%20Bank%E2%80%99s%20assistant%20general%20manager%20of%20the%20financial%20inclusion%20department%2C%20Joydeep%20Nandy%2C%20sent%20the%20following%20reply%3A%20%E2%80%9CIn%20our%20communication%20to%20our%20zonal%20offices%2C%20we%20clearly%20mentioned%20that%20the%20customers%20should%20be%20contacted%20and%20persuaded%20to%20get%20enrolled%20under%20PMJJBY%20and%20PMSBY.%20We%20also%20mentioned%20that%20due%20procedure%20of%20PMJJBY%20and%20PMSBY%20enrolments%20like%20obtaining%20consent%20forms%2C%20nominee%20details%20etc.%20should%20be%20followed%20by%20branches%20before%20enrolment%20of%20customers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENandy%20said%20a%20bulk%20enrolment%20menu%20was%20especially%20devised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20light%20of%20the%20above%2C%20we%20have%20not%20followed%20any%20unethical%20practice%20while%20enrolling%20customers%20under%20both%20the%20schemes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bank%E2%80%99s%20customers%20have%20been%20stating%20otherwise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F26162226%2FUntitled-2.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22790%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F26162226%2FUntitled-2.jpeg%20790w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F26162226%2FUntitled-2-300x117.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-703269%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22307%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EArticle%2014%3C%2Fb%3E%C2%A0discussed%20these%20allegations%20with%20forensic%20accountant%20and%20certified%20fraud%20examiner%20Nikhil%20Parulkar%2C%20a%20co-founder%20of%20forensic%20advisory%20services%20firm%20Ocurisc%20Consulting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20UCO%20Bank%20employee%20union%E2%80%99s%20letter%2C%20employees%E2%80%99%20allegations%20and%20online%20complaints%20are%20material%20enough%20to%20warrant%20an%20internal%2Fforensic%20investigation%2C%20which%20would%20entail%20checking%20with%20customers%20whether%20they%20were%20enrolled%20with%20or%20without%20their%20consent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParulkar%20said%20the%20first%20step%20would%20be%20to%20order%20an%20immediate%20stop%20to%20debiting%20customers%E2%80%99%20accounts%20for%20the%20schemes.%20Then%20the%20bank%E2%80%99s%20internal%20audit%20team%20or%20the%20vigilance%20department%20should%20check%20with%2010%E2%80%9315%25%20of%20randomly%20selected%20customers%20whether%20they%20were%20enrolled%20with%20or%20without%20their%20consent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECanara%20Bank%2C%20SBI%20and%20Bank%20of%20Baroda%20did%20not%20reply%20to%C2%A0%3Cb%3EArticle%2014%3C%2Fb%3E%E2%80%99s%20questions%20about%20enrolling%20customers%20without%20their%20knowledge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20January%202024%C2%A0%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.moneycontrol.com%2Fnews%2Fbusiness%2Fsbi-warns-staff-against-enrolling-customers-in-insurance-schemes-without-consent-12126301.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%C2%A0%3Ci%3EMoneyControl%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0showed%20that%20the%20SBI%20was%20aware%20of%20the%20problem%20and%20had%20issued%20a%20letter%20in%20this%20regard%2C%20instructing%C2%A0%20branches%20to%20desist%20from%20%E2%80%9Csuch%20unethical%20practices%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParulkar%20said%20the%20problem%20of%20debiting%20customers%E2%80%99%20accounts%20without%20permission%20for%20one%20or%20the%20other%20schemes%20is%20a%20common%20ailment%2C%20called%20predatory%20sales%20practices%20in%20forensic%20audit%20parlance.%20He%20said%20such%20scenarios%20are%20prevalent%20in%20the%20banking%20sector%2C%20including%20private%20sector%20banks%2C%20but%20don%E2%80%99t%20get%20exposed%20until%20a%20whistleblower%20comes%20forth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ECanara%20Bank%E2%80%99s%20Cover-Up%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECanara%20Bank%20underwent%20an%20audit%20in%20December%202023%20after%20an%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fwealth%2Fpersonal-finance-news%2Fsbi-canara-bank-deducting-premiums-for-govt-insurance-schemes-from-savings-accounts-without-consent-complaints-flood-x%2Farticleshow%2F105646894.cms%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%C2%A0%3Ci%3EThe%20Economic%20Times%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0highlighted%20online%20complaints%20about%20unauthorised%20debits%20for%20PMJJBY%20and%20PMSBY.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bank%E2%80%99s%20employees%E2%80%99%20grapevine%20was%20abuzz%20with%20news%20about%20this%20audit.%20Purportedly%2C%20the%20government%20asked%20the%20bank%E2%80%99s%20leadership%20to%20look%20into%20the%20allegations.%20Subsequently%2C%20branches%20were%20asked%20to%20examine%20customers%E2%80%99%20application%20forms%20for%20these%20schemes.%20Since%20many%20customers%20were%20enrolled%20without%20consent%20via%20bulk%20activation%2C%20their%20forms%20did%20not%20exist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20employee%20said%20his%20regional%20manager%E2%80%94the%20very%20official%20who%20had%20enrolled%20customers%20without%20permission%20in%20bulk%E2%80%94advised%20branch%20heads%20during%20a%20video%20conference%20to%20give%20a%20fake%20confirmation%20that%20the%20forms%20were%20all%20in%20place.%20The%20employee%20said%20his%20branch%20did%20just%20that.%20Eventually%2C%20its%20claim%20was%20accepted%20on%20face%20value%20and%20not%20cross-checked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EArticle%2014%3C%2Fb%3E%C2%A0has%20a%20copy%20of%20an%20email%20sent%20by%20a%20regional%20office%20of%20the%20bank%20to%20employees%20about%20the%20audit.%20Sent%20on%2029%20December%202023%2C%20it%20says%3A%20%E2%80%9CAll%20employees%20are%20advised%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20consent%20forms%20in%20respect%20of%20PMJJBY%20and%20PMSBY%20enrolled%20accounts%20are%20obtained%20and%20placed%20on%20records.%20Inspection%20wing%20has%20given%20a%20timeline%20up%20to%2030.12.2023%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20consent%20letter%20from%20customers%20has%20been%20obtained%20invariably%20and%20kept%20on%20record.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20former%20branch%20manager%20of%20Canara%20Bank%20posted%20in%20central%20India%20recounted%20that%20a%20couple%20of%20years%20ago%2C%20his%20regional%20office%20enrolled%2050-odd%20customers%20of%20his%20branch%20in%20PMJJBY%20from%20the%20back-end%2C%20without%20consent.%20He%20said%20that%20to%20save%20himself%20from%20any%20trouble%20later%20on%2C%20he%20obtained%20application%20forms%20from%20most%20of%20the%20customers%20over%20the%20next%20few%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20aforesaid%20audit%20that%20followed%C2%A0%3Ci%3EThe%20Economic%20Times%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0report%2C%20Canara%20Bank%20employees%20were%20required%20to%20pull%20off%20a%20similar%20feat%2C%20in%20one%20day.%20About%20two%20weeks%20after%20the%20bank%20asked%20its%20employees%20over%20email%20to%20obtain%20consent%20forms%2C%20a%20bank%20officer%20told%C2%A0%3Cb%3EArticle%2014%3C%2Fb%3E%C2%A0via%20WhatsApp%20that%20the%20management%20was%20turning%20on%20the%20heat.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20application%20pressure%20is%20real.%20I%20feel%20like%20resigning%20%5Bfrom%5D%20the%20job.%20What%20the%20heck!%20Someone%20from%20the%20back-end%20did%20something%2C%20now%20they%20are%20asking%20us%20to%20clean%20that%20mess.%20How%20am%20I%20going%20to%20get%204%2C000%20forms!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20employee%20later%20said%20she%20did%20not%20arrange%20for%20the%20forms%20as%20the%20pressure%20for%20the%20same%20vanished.%20Canara%20Bank%20did%20not%20reply%20to%C2%A0%3Cb%3EArticle%2014%3C%2Fb%3E%E2%80%99s%20questions%20about%20this%20audit%20and%20the%20aforesaid%20email.%20Forensic%20auditor%20Parulkar%20said%20the%20email%20unambiguously%20pointed%20at%20wrongdoing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWherever%20we%20have%20enrolled%20without%20asking%2C%20create%20a%20paper%20trail%20for%20that%20and%20place%20it%20on%20record.%20That%20is%20how%20this%20email%20has%20to%20be%20read%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20this%20is%20a%20fraudulent%20practice%20tantamount%20to%20doctoring%20a%20document.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EPressure%20From%20The%20Top%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20this%20pressure%2C%20bank%20employees%20do%20not%20blame%20their%20management%20as%20much%20as%20they%20blame%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffinancialservices.gov.in%2Fbeta%2Fen%2Fpage%2Foverview%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDepartment%20of%20Financial%20Services%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0(DFS)%2C%20which%20is%20in%20charge%20of%20key%20initiatives%20of%20the%20government%20concerning%20the%20banking%20and%20insurance%20sectors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20PMJJBY%2C%20PMSBY%2C%20APY%20and%20other%20government%20schemes%2C%20the%20DFS%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDFS_India%2Fstatus%2F1758119464762028102%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egives%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0enrolment%20targets%20to%20banks.%20Bank%20employees%20told%C2%A0%3Cb%3EArticle%2014%3C%2Fb%3E%C2%A0that%20top%20executives%20are%20berated%20by%20the%20DFS%20and%20threatened%20with%20consequences%20for%20failing%20to%20meet%20the%20targets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20recent%20letter%20issued%20by%20government-run%20Punjab%20%26amp%3B%20Sind%20Bank%20to%20a%20zonal%20manager%20illustrates%20this%20top-down%20pressure.%20The%20letter%20cites%20the%20DFS%E2%80%99s%20order%20about%20these%20insurance%20and%20pension%20schemes%2C%20notes%20that%20the%20zonal%20manager%E2%80%99s%20area%20is%20lagging%20behind%2C%20and%20ends%20with%20a%20warning%3A%20the%20targets%20are%20to%20be%20%E2%80%9Cmandatorily%20achieved%E2%80%9D%20to%20avoid%20%E2%80%9Cany%20unpleasant%20action%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20497px)%2085vw%2C%20497px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F26162327%2FUntitled-3.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22497%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F26162327%2FUntitled-3.jpeg%20954w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F26162327%2FUntitled-3-300x294.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-703270%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22487%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EBank%20employees%20point%20out%20that%20the%20order%20to%20achieve%20a%20lion%E2%80%99s%20share%20of%20the%20yearly%20target%20in%20just%20two%20weeks%20is%20bound%20to%20lead%20to%20unethical%20and%2For%20illegal%20solutions.%20Photo%20courtesy%20Article%2014%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EArticle%2014%3C%2Fb%3E%C2%A0also%20has%20audio-video%20clips%20of%20a%20performance%20review%20meeting%20of%20Union%20Bank%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20Ayodhya%20region%20from%20November%202022.%20In%20the%20meeting%2C%20the%20bank%E2%80%99s%20regional%20head%20was%20rebuking%20branch%20managers%20for%20not%20meeting%20their%20enrolment%20targets%20for%20PMJJBY%20and%20PMSBY.%20%E2%80%9COn%20December%201%2C%20MD%20%26amp%3B%20CEO%20has%20a%20meeting%20with%20the%20Department%20of%20Financial%20Services.%20Secondly%2C%20the%20%5BUnion%5D%20Finance%20Minister%20will%20do%20the%20review%20herself%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20regional%20head%20is%20heard%20saying%20sternly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELikewise%2C%C2%A0%3Cb%3EArticle%2014%3C%2Fb%3E%C2%A0has%20seen%20screenshots%20of%20bank%20employees%E2%80%99%20WhatsApp%20groups%20wherein%20senior%20managers%20bring%20up%20the%20DFS%E2%80%99s%20name%20to%20push%20their%20staff%20to%20achieve%20enrolment%20targets.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20this%20is%20a%20DFS%20requirement%2C%20please%20drive%20maximum%20business%20today%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20one%20such%20message.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20pressure%20tactic%20is%20used%20not%20only%20on%20bank%20employees%20but%20also%20on%20business%20correspondents%E2%80%94independent%20service-providers%20who%20run%20banking%20kiosks%20or%20mini-branches%20in%20remote%20regions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20SBI%20kiosk%20operator%20from%20rural%20Bihar%20told%20this%20reporter%20that%20his%20seniors%20have%20been%20ordering%20every%20day%20in%20online%20meetings%20to%20meet%20the%20targets%20assigned%20by%20the%20DFS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20seniors%20advise%20arm-twisting%20customers%20into%20signing%20up%20and%20also%20threaten%20kiosk%20operators%20with%20loss%20of%20pay.%C2%A0%3Cb%3EArticle%2014%3C%2Fb%3E%E2%80%99s%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farticle-14.com%2Fpost%2Fhow-an-aadhaar-fraud-forces-the-poor-into-paying-for-welfare-schemes-they-do-not-want-63f57eb9e8d15%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprevious%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0explains%20how%20these%20dynamics%20lead%20to%20widespread%20fraud%20with%20rural%20customers.%20A%20report%20in%20Hindi%20daily%C2%A0%3Ci%3EDainik%20Bhaskar%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0on%2017%20March%20described%20how%20an%20SBI%20kiosk%20operator%20in%20rural%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20fraudulently%20enrolled%20customers%20in%20PMSBY%20and%20registered%20their%20dead%20fathers%20as%20nominees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EArticle%2014%3C%2Fb%3E%C2%A0sought%20comment%20from%20the%20DFS%20and%20the%20union%20finance%20ministry%20via%20email%20on%202%20March.%20There%20was%20no%20reply.%20If%20there%20is%20a%20response%2C%20we%20will%20update%20this%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EArticle%2014%3C%2Fb%3E%C2%A0filed%20an%20RTI%20request%20with%20the%20department%20and%20sought%20a%20copy%20of%20its%20letters%2Fcirculars%20to%20banks%20regarding%20enrollment%20under%20PMJJBY%2C%20PMSBY%20and%20APY.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20refused%20the%20information%20on%20the%20grounds%20that%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20information%20sought%20is%20under%20deliberation%20with%20the%20concerned%20stakeholders.%20The%20information%20received%20or%20generated%20is%20in%20fiduciary%20capacity%20and%20is%20likely%20to%20affect%20and%20compromise%20the%20strategic%20and%20economic%20interests%20of%20the%20State.%20The%20disclosure%20of%20such%20information%20is%20likely%20to%20affect%20the%20decision-making%20of%20the%20authority.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmployees%20of%20various%20government%20banks%20explained%20to%C2%A0%3Cb%3EArticle%2014%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3Ehow%20the%20pressure%20for%20these%20schemes%20percolates%20from%20the%20management%20to%20ground-level%20staff%20and%20results%20in%20fraud.%20Requesting%20anonymity%2C%20a%20mid-level%20officer%20of%20a%20government%20bank%20recounted%20a%20first-hand%20experience%20from%20his%20stint%20in%20a%20regional%20office%3A%20high%20enrolment%20targets%20for%20PMJJBY%20and%20PMSBY%20were%20imposed%20upon%20managers%2C%20eight%20of%20whom%20fell%20short%2C%20so%20they%20were%20lambasted%20in%20a%20meeting%20and%20their%20salary%20docked%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20once%20discussed%20with%20his%20senior%2C%20an%20assistant%20general%20manager%2C%20his%20apprehensions%20about%20debiting%20customers%E2%80%99%20accounts%20without%20consent.%20He%20said%20the%20official%20dismissed%20his%20concerns%20and%20told%20him%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Ci%3EKya%20fark%20padta%20hai!%20Kuch%20nahi%20hoga.%20Sab%20upar%20se%20neeche%20tak%20government%20ka%20saath%20hai%3C%2Fi%3E.%E2%80%9D%20(How%20does%20it%20matter!%20Nothing%20will%20happen.%20From%20the%20top%20to%20the%20bottom%2C%20we%20have%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20backing.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20gauge%20the%20extent%20of%20fraudulent%20enrolments%2C%20this%20reporter%20created%20a%20poll%20in%20three%20Facebook%20groups%20of%20bank%20employees.%20One%20group%20was%20the%20bank