gcaption%3ECard%20giants%20Visa%20and%20Mastercard%20struck%20a%20settlement%20after%20years%20of%20legal%20wrangling.%3Cp%3EPicture%20alliance%2FGetty%20Images%3B%20Jenny%20Chang-Rodriguez%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EVisa%20and%20Mastercard%20settled%20a%20dispute%20with%20US%20retailers%20over%20credit-card%20swipe%20fees.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20settlement%20could%20ultimately%20affect%20credit-card%20reward%20programs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBanks%20aren't%20likely%20to%20abandon%20rewards%20programs%2C%20but%20they%20could%20get%20less%20rewarding.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20great%20American%20pastimes%20%E2%80%94%20using%20your%20credit%20card%20to%20accumulate%20points%20%E2%80%94%20could%20be%20about%20to%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvisa-mastercard-lawsuit-settlement-credit-card-fees-checkout-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVisa%20and%20Mastercard%20settled%20with%20US%20retailers%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20a%20longstanding%20dispute%20tied%20to%20credit-card%20swipe%20fees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20crux%20of%20the%20issue%20is%20interchange%20fees%2C%20which%20networks%20like%20Visa%20and%20Mastercard%20charge%20merchants%20for%20processing%20their%20transactions.%20Under%20the%20agreement%2C%20which%20still%20needs%20to%20be%20approved%20by%20the%20courts%2C%20these%20fees%20would%20be%20lowered%20and%20capped%20for%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20what%20does%20that%20have%20to%20do%20with%20your%20sacred%20stash%20of%20points%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20the%20networks%20set%20interchange%20fees%2C%20the%20card%20issuers%20(banks%20like%20JPMorgan%20Chase%20and%20Bank%20of%20America)%20get%20the%20lion's%20share%20of%20the%20revenue.%20Last%20year%20the%20biggest%20US%20banks%20took%20home%20%2431%20billion%20of%20interchange%20and%20merchant%20processing%20income%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2024-03-26%2Fvisa-mastercard-reach-30-billion-swipe-fee-deal-with-merchants%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20Bloomberg%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAgain%2C%20you%20ask%2C%20what%20does%20that%20have%20to%20do%20with%20%3Cem%3Emy%20points%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWell%2C%20a%20good%20chunk%20of%20that%20revenue%20is%20spent%20by%20banks%20encouraging%20you%20to%20use%20their%20fancy%20cards.%20And%20the%20best%20way%20to%20do%20that%20is%20via%20points%20and%20rewards.%20Cards%20with%20better%20rewards%20and%20cash-back%20economics%20typically%20charge%20higher%20interchange%20fees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhich%20gets%20us%20back%20to%20Tuesday's%20settlement.%20Merchants%20have%20to%20accept%20all%20types%20of%20credit%20cards%20from%20Visa%20and%20Mastercard%20under%20an%20%26quot%3Bhonor%20all%20cards%26quot%3B%20rule.%20But%20now%2C%20they'd%20be%20able%20to%20charge%20consumers%20more%20depending%20on%20the%20type%20of%20card%20they're%20using.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuddenly%2C%20the%20cash-back%20you%20get%20from%20your%20Chase%20Sapphire%20Reserve%20doesn't%20seem%20as%20enticing%20when%20paying%20a%20premium%20on%20the%20bacon-egg-and-cheese%20sandwich%20at%20your%20local%20bodega.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20likely%20that%20banks%20will%20completely%20punt%20on%20rewards.%20David%20Morris%2C%20principal%20analyst%2C%20payments%20at%20eMarketer%2C%20said%20the%20card%20programs%20are%20too%20important%20to%20banks%20to%20stop%20engaging%20those%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20can%20make%20allowances%20of%20their%20own%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20kinds%20of%20rewards%2C%20adjusting%20the%20rewards%20accordingly.%20These%20are%20highly%20profitable%20programs%2C%20so%20there%20is%20some%20flexibility%20here%20for%20the%20card%20companies%20to%20be%20able%20to%20make%20some%20adjustments%20along%20those%20lines%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMorris%20acknowledged%20that%20some%20changes%20in%20consumer%20behavior%20might%20occur%20as%20a%20result%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20that%20would%20discount%20the%20levers%20that%20these%20credit%20card%20issuers%20do%20have%20to%20be%20able%20to%20ensure%20that%20they%20are%20providing%20the%20card%20value%20that%20premium%20cardholders%20expect.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMerchants%2C%20especially%20retailers%2C%20don't%20seem%20pleased%20with%20the%20settlement.%20The%20National%20Retail%20Federation%2C%20which%20represents%20chains%20from%20big%20box%20stores%20to%20supermarkets%2C%20said%20it%20%26quot%3Bamounts%20to%20pennies%20on%20the%20dollar%26quot%3B%20toward%20their%20costs.%20And%20the%20Retail%20Industry%20Leaders%20Association%20called%20it%20%26quot%3Ba%20mere%20drop%20in%20the%20bucket.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20trade%20groups%20expressed%20support%20on%20Tuesday%20for%20the%20Credit%20Card%20Competition%20Act%20before%20Congress%2C%20which%20would%20require%20large%20banks%20to%20offer%20multiple%20payment%20networks%20for%20processing%20transactions%20through%20their%20credit%20cards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20many%20small%20businesses%20already%20charge%20an%20extra%20fee%20for%20those%20paying%20with%20a%20credit%20card%2C%20David%20Silverman%2C%20a%20senior%20director%20at%20Fitch%20Ratings%2C%20said%20most%20major%20retailers%20won't%20pass%20the%20interchange%20costs%20directly%20to%20consumers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20retailers%20have%20been%20absorbing%20costs%20across%20any%20number%20of%20cost%20functions%2C%26quot%3B%20such%20as%20labor%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20yet%20clear%20what%20impact%20the%20settlement%20will%20have.%20The%20agreement%20hasn't%20yet%20been%20approved%2C%20and%20time%20will%20tell%20how%20merchants%20and%20banks%20handle%20the%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20points%20game%20can%20be%20one%20of%20fine%20margins%2C%20and%20a%20change%20to%20interchange%20fees%20could%20have%20ripple%20effects%20for%20rewards%20programs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDon't%20be%20surprised%20if%20it%20starts%20taking%20a%20lot%20longer%20to%20rack%20up%20the%20points%20required%20for%20your%20next%20getaway.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvisa-mastercard-merchants-agreement-impacts-credit-cards-reward-programs-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711489037000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66031d443f923f7dab0174c0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvisa-mastercard-merchants-agreement-impacts-credit-cards-reward-programs-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20cap%20on%20interchange%20fees%20might%20mean%20a%20shift%20in%20how%20consumers%20earn%20points%20on%20transactions.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ddefrancesco%40businessinsider.com%20(Dan%20DeFrancesco%2CAlex%20Bitter)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A80%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvisa-mastercard-merchants-agreement-impacts-credit-cards-reward-programs-2024-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22See%20Marines%20handle%20tarantulas%20and%20vipers%20to%20be%20ready%20to%20fight%20in%20the%20jungle%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Royal%20Thai%20Marine%20instructor%20kisses%20the%20head%20of%20a%20Monocled%20Cobra%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6601cd8f16bde8d4ead1eb59%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Royal%20Thai%20Marine%20instructor%20kisses%20the%20head%20of%20a%20Monocled%20Cobra%20during%20a%20jungle%20survival%20demonstration%20at%20Exercise%20Cobra%20Gold%20in%20Sattahip%2C%20Chonburi%20province%2C%20Thailand.%3Cp%3EUS%20Marine%20Corps%20photo%20by%20Sgt.%20Patrick%20Katz%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThai%20and%20US%20Marines%20confronted%20deadly%20jungle%20creatu