p%3EWhile%20the%20target%20of%20the%20raid%20has%20not%20yet%20been%20identified%20and%20Combs%20has%20not%20been%20arrested%20as%20of%20Tuesday%2C%20it%20was%20the%20latest%20and%20most%20serious%20event%20in%20ongoing%20legal%20troubles%20facing%20the%20music%20mogul%2C%20who%20is%20best%20known%20as%20Diddy.%20Over%20the%20past%20five%20months%2C%20sexual%20assault%20and%20misconduct%20allegations%20have%20piled%20up%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20November%2C%20an%20ex-girlfriend%20of%20Combs'%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsean-combs-diddy-sex-trafficking-rape-abuse-lawsuit-cassie-venutura-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECasandra%20Ventura%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20filed%20a%20lawsuit%20accusing%20him%20of%20sexual%20assault%20and%20abuse%20during%20the%2010%20years%20they%20dated.%20Combs%20denied%20the%20allegations%20and%20Ventura%2C%20known%20as%20Cassie%2C%20settled%20with%20Combs%20a%20day%20after%20she%20filed%20the%20lawsuit.%20Still%2C%20additional%20women%20soon%20came%20forward%20with%20their%20own%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftimeline-sean-diddy-combs-sexual-misconduct-timeline-2024-2%23november-16-2023-ventura-files-the-first-lawsuit-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eallegations%20of%20rape%2C%20sex%20trafficking%2C%20and%20sexual%20abuse%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20February%2C%20music%20producer%20Rodney%20Jones%20Jr.%2C%20also%20known%20as%20Lil%20Rod%2C%20filed%20a%20lawsuit%20accusing%20Combs%20of%20groping%20him%20and%20forcing%20him%20to%20perform%20sexual%20acts%20with%20sex%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECombs%20has%20denied%20all%20the%20prior%20allegations%20against%20him.%20In%20response%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider%20following%20Monday's%20raids%2C%20his%20attorney%20Aaron%20Dyer%20said%20in%20a%20statement%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMr.%20Combs%20was%20never%20detained%20but%20spoke%20to%20and%20cooperated%20with%20authorities.%20Despite%20media%20speculation%2C%20neither%20Mr.%20Combs%20nor%20any%20of%20his%20family%20members%20have%20been%20arrested%20nor%20has%20their%20ability%20to%20travel%20been%20restricted%20in%20any%20way.%20This%20unprecedented%20ambush%20%E2%80%94%20paired%20with%20an%20advanced%2C%20coordinated%20media%20presence%20%E2%80%94%20leads%20to%20a%20premature%20rush%20to%20judgment%20of%20Mr.%20Combs%20and%20is%20nothing%20more%20than%20a%20witch%20hunt%20based%20on%20meritless%20accusations%20made%20in%20civil%20lawsuits.%20There%20has%20been%20no%20finding%20of%20criminal%20or%20civil%20liability%20with%20any%20of%20these%20allegations.%20Mr.%20Combs%20is%20innocent.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDiddy%20operates%20in%20a%20world%20of%20extreme%20wealth.%20In%20the%20three%20decades%20since%20he%20started%20Bad%20Boy%20Records%2C%20the%2054-year-old%20has%20amassed%20more%20money%20than%20nearly%20any%20other%20hip-hop%20artist.%20He%20pioneered%20a%20business%20playbook%20that%20has%20been%20followed%20by%20many%20other%20successful%20musicians%20and%20became%20an%20industry%20gatekeeper%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0giving%20him%20power%20that%20several%20of%20the%20people%20suing%20him%20accuse%20him%20of%20using%20to%20cover%20up%20his%20abuse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ERecords%2C%20fashion%2C%20liquor%3A%20Combs%20pioneered%20the%20hip-hop%20money-making%20playbook.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%201993%2C%20Combs%2C%20then%20known%20as%20Puff%20Daddy%20and%20Puffy%2C%20founded%20Bad%20Boy%20Records%20after%20a%20stint%20at%20Uptown%20Records.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20label%20soon%20became%20%3Cem%3Ethe%20%3C%2Fem%3Eplace%20for%20East%20Coast%20hip-hop%20acts%20emerging%20on%20the%20scene.%20He%20signed%20Craig%20Mack%2C%20112%2C%20Faith%20Evans%2C%20Mase%2C%20and%20The%20Notorious%20B.I.G.%20Combs'%20own%201997%20album%20%26quot%3BNo%20Way%20Out%26quot%3B%20reached%20platinum%20status%20seven%20times%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20heyday%2C%20the%20label%20brought%20in%20%241