e%20became%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-jay-z-and-diddy-made-millions-off-of-cheap-alcohol-zack-omalley-greenburg-2018-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebrand%20ambassador%20for%20Ciroc%20vodka%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20struck%20up%20a%20unique%20deal%20with%20Diageo%20and%20got%20paid%20per%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithin%20the%20first%20two%20years%20of%20the%20partnership%2C%20annual%20sales%20grew%20from%2075%2C000%20to%20400%2C000%20cases%2C%20according%20to%20a%20lawsuit%20Combs%20filed%20against%20Diageo%20last%20year.%20In%202014%2C%20it%20sold%202.6%20million.%20The%20liquor%20giant%20doubled%20down%20on%20Combs%2C%20announcing%20in%202014%20that%20they'd%20bought%20DeLeon%20tequila%20in%20a%2050-50%20partnership.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Combs%20and%20Diageo%20parted%20ways%20earlier%20this%20year%20after%20a%20contentious%20legal%20battle%2C%20the%20company%20did%20give%20some%20insight%20into%20Combs'%20total%20earnings%20in%20a%20court%20filing%20last%20year%3A%20He'd%20made%20nearly%20a%20billion%20dollars%20throughout%20their%2015-year%20partnership.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20invested%20that%20money%20in%20other%20upstarts%2C%20launching%20the%20Revolt%20TV%20cable%20network%20in%202013%20and%20teaming%20with%20Mark%20Wahlberg%20to%20purchase%20a%20majority%20stake%20in%20water%20company%20Aquahydrate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20the%20numbers%20don't%20lie%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fzackomalleygreenburg%2F2013%2F06%2F20%2Fdiddy-talks-cable-deal-will-it-make-him-a-billionaire%2F%3Fsh%3D25a9d4346a0e%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EForbes%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20year.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20just%20like%20any%20other%20businessman%3B%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year%20I%20have%20to%20get%20my%20report%20card%20and%20deal%20with%20the%20reality%20of%20whatever%20it%20is.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Diddy%20Ciroc%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6603245c1caec1275a69b1cf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222143%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDiddy's%20partnership%20with%20Ciroc%20was%20his%20most%20lucrative%20income%20stream.%20He%20earned%20tens%20of%20millions%20a%20year%20for%20promoting%20the%20brand.%3Cp%3EEthan%20Miller%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%202022%2C%20Combs%20was%20labeled%20a%20billionaire%20for%20the%20first%20time.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%201999%20interview%2C%20Combs%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fforbes%2F1999%2F0322%2F6306180a.html%3Fsh%3D486adb752354%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EForbes%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20he%20%26quot%3Bwanted%20to%20be%20very%2C%20very%20rich.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20exactly%20what%20happened.%20By%202022%2C%20Combs'%20net%20worth%20had%20reached%20%241%20billion%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fzogblog.substack.com%2Fp%2Fhip-hops-wealthiest-artists-2022%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EZack%20O'Malley%20Greenburg%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20author%20of%20the%20Jay-Z%20biography%20%26quot%3BEmpire%20State%20of%20Mind%2C%26quot%3B%20who%20tracks%20hip-hop's%20wealthiest%20musicians.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20that%20figure%20has%20likely%20fallen%20over%20the%20past%20year%20%E2%80%94%20he's%20given%20up%20the%20publishing%20rights%20for%20Bad%20Boy's%20artists%2C%20and%20his%20deal%20with%20Diageo%20has%20been%20dissolved%20%E2%80%94%20his%20wealth%20is%20still%20massive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECombined%2C%20he's%20earned%20well%20over%20%241%20billion%2C%20pretax%2C%20from%20the%20Ciroc%20deal%2C%20his%20record%20label%2C%20and%20Sean%20John.%20Some%20of%20that%20is%20tied%20up%20in%20various%20investments%20%E2%80%94%20including%20less-than-successful%20ones%2C%20like%20Revolt%20TV%20%E2%80%94%20while%20a%20significant%20amount%20has%20been%20spent%20on%20a%20life%20of%20luxury%20and%20various%20toys.%20He%20owns%20a%20jet%20that%20costs%20eight%20figures%2C%20over%20%241%20million%20worth%20of%20jewelry%2C%20and%20a%20collection%20of%20art%20that%20includes%20a%20%2421%20million%20painting%20by%20Kerry%20James%20Marshall%20and%20works%20by%20Andy%20Warhol%2C%20Keith%20Haring%2C%20and%20Jean-Michel%20Basquiat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20real%20estate%20portfolio%20includes%20immense%20properties%20in%20Los%20Angeles%20and%20Miami%2C%20worth%20%2446%20million%20and%20%2436%20million%2C%20respectively%2C%20according%20to%20county%20assessments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWhile%20building%20his%20empire%2C%20Combs%20amassed%20%26quot%3Bdangerous%26quot%3B%20power.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECombs%20has%20accumulated%20a%20combination%20of%20wealth%20and%20influence%20from%20his%20various%20business%20endeavors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20has%20made%20him%20%26quot%3Bimmensely%20powerful%2C%20and%20immensely%20dangerous%2C%26quot%3B%20Ventura's%20attorney%20wrote%20in%20her%20complaint%20against%20Combs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20%26quot%3Bused%20his%20money%20and%20power%20to%20orchestrate%20extensive%20efforts%20to%20hide%20the%20evidence%20of%20his%20abuse%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20complaint%20continues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20complaint%20alleges%20Combs%20%26quot%3Blured%26quot%3B%20Ventura%20into%20his%20circle%2C%20using%20his%20position%20as%20the%20head%20of%20Bad%20Boy%20Records.%20Ventura%20said%20after%20the%20abuse%20started%2C%20Combs%20used%20his%20money%20and%20power%20to%20hide%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20often%20afraid%20to%20fight%20back%20or%20speak%20up%2C%20knowing%20he%20had%20a%20powerful%20network%20who%20would%20defend%20him%2C%20according%20to%20the%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20no%20one%20she%20could%20tell%20about%20what%20had%20happened%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20this%20incredibly%20powerful%20man%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20complaint%20says.%20%26quot%3BShe%20recognized%20that%20she%20was%20powerless%2C%20and%20that%20reporting%20Mr.%20Combs%20to%20the%20authorities%20would%20not%20alter%20Mr.%20Combs's%20status%20or%20influence%20but%20would%20merely%20give%20Mr.%20Combs%20another%20excuse%20to%20hurt%20her.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20separate%20lawsuit%20filed%20in%20November%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsean-combs-diddy-sexual-assault-lawsuit-joi-dickerson-neal-cassie-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJoi%20Dickerson-Neal%20alleges%20that%20Combs%20drugged%20and%20assaulted%3C%2Fa%3E%20her%20in%201991.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%2C%20at%20the%20time%2C%20she%20tried%20to%20take%20legal%20action%2C%20%26quot%3Bcolleagues%20told%20Plaintiff%20that%20they%20were%20terrified%20that%20Combs%20would%20retaliate%20against%20them%20and%20that%20they%20would%20lose%20future%20business%20and%20music%20opportunities%20if%20they%20made%20a%20statement%20in%20support%20of%20Plaintiff%2C%20as%20Combs'%20star%20was%20on%20the%20rise%20in%20the%201990s%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20complaint%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%20another%20lawsuit%2C%20filed%20in%20December%20by%20an%20unnamed%20woman%20only%20identified%20as%20Jane%20Doe%2C%20accuses%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdiddy-gang-raped-high-schooler-lawsuit-alleges-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECombs%20of%20using%20a%20private%20jet%20to%20aid%20in%20the%20sex%20trafficking%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20gang%20rape%20of%20a%20high%20school%20student.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20feds%20storming%20his%20properties%20and%20allegations%20mounting%2C%20it%20seems%20as%20if%20Combs'%20reign%20as%20a%20hip-hop%20powerhouse%20may%20be%20coming%20to%20an%20end%20%E2%80%94%20in%20part%20due%20to%20the%20lawsuits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20claims%20of%20sexual%20assault%2C%20Combs%20stepped%20down%20as%20Revolt's%20chairman%20and%20has%20reportedly%20sold%20his%20shares.%20Hulu%20canceled%20a%20re