-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-68667556.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-68667556.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Punjab%3A%20Congress%20Leaders%20Continue%20to%20Move%20to%20BJP%3B%20Ravneet%20Bittu%20is%20Latest%20Deserter%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F26220910%2FBittu-FI.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChandigarh%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Congress%20leader%20and%20Ludhiana%20MP%20Ravneet%20Bittu%2C%2048%2C%20is%20the%20latest%20addition%20to%20a%20growing%20list%20of%20Congress%20leaders%20leaving%20the%20party%20to%20begin%20new%20innings%20in%20the%20BJP%20in%20Punjab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20top%20leadership%20currently%20in%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Punjab%20unit%20are%20former%20Congress%20state%20chief%20Sunil%20Jakhar%20and%20senior%20leaders%20like%20Captain%20Amarinder%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20Amarinder%E2%80%99s%20wife%20Praneet%20Kaur%2C%20who%20was%20Congress%20MP%20from%20Patiala%2C%20also%20joined%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBittu%2C%20a%20three-time%20MP%2C%20also%20comes%20from%20a%20prominent%20Congress%20family.%20His%20grandfather%2C%20Beant%20Singh%2C%20a%20former%20CM%20of%20Punjab%20between%201992%20and%201995%2C%20was%20assassinated%20during%20the%20Khalistan%20militancy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20brother%20Gurkirat%20Singh%20Kotli%20is%20still%20a%20Congress%20MLA%20from%20Khanna%2C%20a%20constituency%20in%20Ludhiana%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBittu%E2%80%99s%20joining%20the%20BJP%20came%20as%20a%20surprise%20for%20many%20as%20there%20was%20nothing%20in%20the%20public%20domain%20to%20suggest%20that%20he%20might%20leave%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20he%20was%20being%20considered%20for%20re-nomination%20from%20Ludhiana%20for%20the%20third%20time%20in%20a%20row%2C%20sources%20in%20the%20Congress%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20believe%20his%20joining%20the%20BJP%20is%20tactical.%20Political%20analyst%20Harjeshwar%20Singh%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20his%20style%20of%20politics%20has%20often%20remained%20close%20to%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20national%20plank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20he%20says%2C%20there%20is%20a%20large%20Hindu%20and%20migrant%20population%20in%20his%20Ludhiana%20constituency%2C%20which%20he%20has%20won%20twice%20in%20a%20row.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20might%20have%20thought%20that%20winning%20the%20seat%20on%20a%20Congress%20ticket%20may%20be%20challenging%20this%20time.%20Therefore%2C%20he%20has%20played%20a%20gamble%20by%20fighting%20as%20a%20BJP%20candidate%20and%20using%20issues%20like%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20and%20the%20Modi%20factor%20to%20sway%20his%20constituency%E2%80%99s%20voters%2C%20Harjeshwar%20Singh%20also%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20reacting%20to%20Bittu%E2%80%99s%20joining%20the%20BJP%2C%20Punjab%20Congress%20president%20Amrinder%20Singh%20Raja%20Warring%20told%20the%20media%20that%20it%20is%20no%20big%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20it%20will%20not%20damage%20the%20party%20and%20that%20such%20deserters%20always%20create%20opportunities%20for%20fresh%20faces%20to%20contest%20and%20carry%20the%20party%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20Bittu%20has%20lost%20far%20more%20significance%20by%20leaving%20the%20party%20his%20family%20served%20with%20their%20blood.%20The%20Congress%20in%20Punjab%20will%20always%20be%20known%20by%20the%20supreme%20sacrifice%20of%20his%20grandfather%2C%20Beant%20Singh.%20He%20%5BBeant%20Singh%5D%20always%20wore%20a%20white%20turban%20and%20was%20a%20strong%20pillar%20of%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20in%20the%20BJP%2C%20Bittu%20will%20just%20be%20another%20MP%20or%20minister%20if%20he%20wins.%20He%20will%20no%20longer%20be%20able%20to%20claim%20his%20identity%20as%20Sardar%20Beant%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20grandson%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Warring.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20Bittu%E2%80%99s%20entire%20family%20is%20still%20devoted%20to%20the%20Congress%20and%20that%20his%20brother%20is%20very%20much%20with%20the%20party%20as%20a%20committed%20worker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20contrary%2C%20Bittu%20said%20during%20his%20media%20briefing%20in%20Delhi%20that%20he%20was%20inspired%20by%20the%20great%20work%20and%20dedication%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20both%20the%20prime%20minister%20and%20the%20home%20minister%20always%20took%20it%20positively%20whenever%20he%20raised%20the%20issues%20of%20Punjab%2C%20and%20that%20he%20wanted%20to%20take%20Punjab%20forward%20but%20no%20other%20than%20the%20BJP%20has%20the%20vision%20to%20do%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20joined%20the%20BJP%20so%20that%20Punjab%20is%20also%20benefited%20like%20the%20rest%20of%20India%20by%20PM%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20development%20agenda%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20performance%20in%20Punjab%20in%20the%20coming%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20he%20said%20a%20record%20number%20of%20BJP%20MPs%20will%20enter%20parliament%20and%20help%20develop%20the%20border%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711471716000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F26220910%2FBittu-FI.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fpunjab-congress-desertions-bjp-ravneet-singh-bittu%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Punjab%20Congress%20chief%20Amrinder%20Singh%20Raja%20Warring%2C%20however%2C%20saw%20no%20damage%20to%20the%20party%2C%20saying%20Bittu's%20switching%20to%20the%20BJP%20will%20create%20space%20for%20new%20people%20to%20contest%20and%20take%20the%20Congress%20forward.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fpunjab-congress-desertions-bjp-ravneet-singh-bittu%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Holi%20at%20North-Eastern%20Hill%20University%20Disrupted%2C%20ABVP%20%E2%80%98Intruders%E2%80%99%20Allegedly%20Involved%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2F15165157%2F1500x500.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20annual%20Holi%20celebration%20at%20the%20North-Eastern%20Hill%20University%20(NEHU)%20in%20Shillong%20typically%20showcases%20the%20spirit%20of%20inclusivity%20and%20communal%20harmony.%20However%2C%20this%20year%E2%80%99s%20festivities%20took%20an%20ugly%20turn%20with%20the%20alleged%20intrusion%20of%20Akhil%20Bharatiya%20Vidyarthi%20Parishad%20(ABVP)%20members.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETheir%20presence%20not%20only%20disrupted%20the%20celebration%2C%20but%20also%20led%20to%20confrontations%20with%20university%20officials%2C%20including%20the%20vice%20president%20of%20NEHU%E2%80%99s%20student%20union%2C%20Easterson%20Sohtun.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESohtun%E2%80%99s%20attempt%20to%20maintain%20order%20and%20inquire%20about%20the%20intruders%E2%80%99%20identity%20was%20met%20with%20hostility%20as%20he%20allegedly%20faced%20casteist%20abuse%20and%20physical%20assault.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CLike%20every%20year%2C%20the%20Holi%20celebrations%20were%20taking%20place%20with%20much%20excitement.%20However%2C%20a%20few%20outsiders%20affiliated%20with%20the%20ABVP%20tried%20to%20take%20political%20mileage%20from%20the%20event%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sonal%20K.S.%2C%20a%20master%E2%80%99s%20student%20in%20Political%20Science%20at%20NEHU%2C%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20the%20safety%20of%20students%20on%20campus%2C%20the%20students%E2%80%99%20union%20vice%20president%20tried%20to%20confront%20the%20intruders.%20It%20was%20then%20that%20he%20faced%20casteist%20abuse.%20He%20was%20also%20beaten%20up%20badly%2C%E2%80%9D%20added%20Sonal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F26210534%2FSohtun-1024x512.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F26210534%2FSohtun-1024x512.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F26210534%2FSohtun-300x150.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F26210534%2FSohtun-800x400.jpg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F26210534%2FSohtun.jpg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-703306%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22420%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESohtun%20was%20allegedly%20assaulted%20by%20ABVP%20members.%20Photos%3A%20Special%20arrangement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CNo%20permission%20given%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20no%20permission%20required%20for%20students%20to%20celebrate%20Holi%20on%20the%20NEHU%20campus%2C%20but%20non-students%20are%20not%20allowed%20to%20do%20the%20same.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAn%20organisation%20named%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.abvp.org%2FWOSY%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EWorld%20Organisation%20of%20Students%20and%20Youth%20(WOSY)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20had%20organised%20the%20Holi%20celebrations%2C%20where%20many%20non-students%20allegedly%20entered%20the%20university.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWOSY%20is%20affiliated%20with%20the%20ABVP.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20North-Eastern%20Hill%20University%20Students%E2%80%99%20Union%