0its%20welfare%20schemes%20are%20not%20reaching%20every%20targeted%20beneficiary.%20Besides%20there%20is%20silent%20dissent%20within%20the%20party%2C%20which%20could%20affect%20its%20poll%20prospects%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mishra%20argued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20it%20is%2C%20pre-poll%20defections%20are%20already%20taking%20place%2C%20with%20the%20BJD%20losing%20two%20sitting%20MLAs%20(both%20had%20been%20expelled%20by%20the%20party)%20and%20two%20former%20MLAs%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20is%20welcoming%20turncoats%20with%20open%20arms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20significant%20is%20that%20state%20leaders%20of%20both%20the%20BJP%20and%20BJD%20appear%20to%20be%20happy%20about%20the%20failure%20of%20the%20alliance%20talks%2C%20which%20they%20have%20termed%20a%20blessing%20in%20disguise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPradeep%20Purohit%2C%20who%20is%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20candidate%20for%20the%20Bargarh%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%2C%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20happy%20that%20alliance%20talks%20collapsed.%20We%20will%20do%20much%20better%20contesting%20the%20polls%20on%20our%20own%20strength.%20We%20are%20going%20ahead%20with%20our%20preparations%20at%20full%20throttle.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParty%20MLA%20from%20Loisingha%2C%20Mukesh%20Mahaling%2C%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20resentment%20among%20our%20workers%20about%20forming%20an%20alliance%20with%20a%20party%20we%20had%20been%20fighting%20for%20the%20last%2015%20years.%20They%20are%20happy%20now%20that%20we%20are%20going%20to%20contest%20on%20our%20own.%20They%20will%20now%20work%20with%20full%20vigour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20will%20be%20a%20neck-to-neck%20fight%20with%20the%20BJD%20and%20we%20may%20even%20form%20a%20government%20in%20the%20state%20on%20our%20own.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJD%20appears%20equally%20confident%20about%20its%20prospects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParty%20general%20secretary%2C%20Bijay%20Nayak%2C%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20failure%20of%20alliance%20talks%20is%20not%20going%20to%20affect%20us%20in%20any%20way.%20In%20fact%2C%20we%20are%20confident%20of%20doing%20much%20better%20by%20contesting%20the%20elections%20on%20our%20own.%20Our%20rivals%20must%20keep%20in%20mind%20that%20the%20popularity%20of%20our%20chief%20minister%20is%20on%20the%20rise.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711463516000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F26195401%2FBJD-BJP.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ffollowing-failure-in-alliance-talks-bjp-and-bjd-gear-up-to-face-each-other-as-rivals%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Leaders%20of%20both%20the%20Odisha%20BJP%20and%20the%20BJD%20appear%20to%20be%20happy%20about%20the%20failure%20of%20the%20alliance%20talks%2C%20which%20they%20have%20termed%20a%20blessing%20in%20disguise.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ffollowing-failure-in-alliance-talks-bjp-and-bjd-gear-up-to-face-each-other-as-rivals%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%228%20Best%20Places%20in%20Bengaluru%20for%20Unforgettable%20Ramzan%20Food%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ECover%20pic%20credits%3A%20Left%20pic%3A%20Instagram%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fusually_chaotic%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERajarshi%20Ghosh%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Right%20pic%3A%20Twitter%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkavashivani%2Fstatus%2F1642145572944744450%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1642145572944744450%257Ctwgr%255Edddb0587c59b521f4815247b5cddce868272ccf9%257Ctwcon%255Es1_%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.lifestyleasia.com%252Find%252Fdining%252Ffood%252Ficonic-bakeries-in-bangalore-that-locals-swear-by%252F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShivani%20Kava%3C%2Fa%