58150%5C%22%3Etargeted%20in%20an%20attack%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0that%20killed%2013%20people%2C%20including%20nine%20Chinese%20nationals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChina%20calls%20for%20%E2%80%98thorough%20investigation%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20said%20it%20%E2%80%9Cstrongly%20condemned%20this%20terrorist%20act%E2%80%9D%20while%20offering%20its%20condolences%20to%20the%20families%20of%20the%20deceased.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Chinese%20embassy%20and%20consulates%20in%20Pakistan%20have%20immediately%20launched%20emergency%20work%2C%20demanding%20that%20the%3Cbr%3E%5CnPakistani%20side%20conduct%20a%20thorough%20investigation%20into%20the%20attack%2C%E2%80%9D%20China%E2%80%99s%20diplomatic%20mission%20in%20Pakistan%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20called%20for%20the%20perpetrators%20of%20the%20attack%C2%A0to%20be%20severely%20punished%20and%20for%20steps%20to%20be%20taken%20to%20protect%20Chinese%20citizens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fis-chinas-investment-in-pakistan-slowing-down%2Fa-67065190%5C%22%3EChina%20has%20invested%20heavily%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20infrastructure%20over%20the%20past%20few%20years%20as%20part%20of%20the%20China%20Pakistan%20Economic%20Corridor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chinese%20projects%20have%20led%20to%20a%20level%20of%20resentment%20in%20some%20local%20quarters%2C%20with%20separatist%20groups%20claiming%20those%20from%20the%20region%20benefit%20little%2C%20with%20most%20jobs%20going%20to%20outsiders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20group%20has%20claimed%20responsibility%20for%20the%C2%A0attack%2C%20but%20Islamist%20militants%20linked%20to%20the%20Pakistani%20Taliban%2C%20known%20as%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fpakistani-taliban-move-into-new-territories%2Fa-65503987%5C%22%3Ethe%20Tehreek-e-Taliban%20Pakistan%20(TTP)%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20have%20previously%20targeted%20Chinese%20interests%20in%20Pakistan.%3C