0target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20homestay%20exudes%20tranquillity.%20%3C%2Fa%3EHowever%2C%20what%20truly%20distinguishes%20it%20is%20the%20deeply%20ingrained%20commitment%20to%20sustainability%20and%20reverence%20for%20nature%20exhibited%20by%20both%20the%20homestay%20and%20its%20hosts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20bought%20this%20land%2C%20traditionally%2C%20there%20is%20a%20%3Cem%3Epuja%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20is%20supposed%20to%20be%20done%20before%20starting%20the%20construction.%20However%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20honour%20nature%20instead%20and%20vowed%20to%20maintain%20it%20just%20as%20it%20is%2C%E2%80%9D%20Alka%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECo-founded%20by%20Alka%20and%20her%20daughter%20Prachi%20Chaphekar%2C%20the%20branding%20at%20the%20property%20is%20managed%20by%20Prachi%2C%20while%20Alka%20oversees%20operations%20and%20other%20duties.%20%E2%80%9CShe%20is%20the%20body%20and%20soul%20of%20Avabodha%20while%20I%20am%20the%20heart%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Prachi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20dream%20of%20a%20lifetime%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20establishing%20the%20homestay%2C%20Alka%20devoted%20decades%20of%20her%20life%20to%20the%20social%20sector.%20She%20saved%20up%20during%20this%20time%20to%20transform%20her%20passion%20for%20helping%20others%20find%20themselves%20into%20a%20reality.%20%E2%80%9CI%20always%20nurtured%20a%20dream%20of%20opening%20my%20own%20space%20where%20people%20could%20come%2C%20relax%2C%20and%20find%20peace%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20ardent%20traveller%2C%20Alka%20found%20the%20perfect%20companion%20in%20her%20daughter%2C%20Prachi.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20I%20loved%20travelling%2C%20my%20husband%20held%20the%20opposite%20view.%20So%2C%20most%20of%20the%20time%2C%20it%20was%20just%20Prachi%20and%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20reminisces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes