3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F11%2F01171239%2Findian-rupee-money-cash.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Indian%20economy%20is%20grappling%20with%20a%20slowdown%20in%20foreign%20direct%20investment%20(FDI).%20In%202022-23%2C%20FDI%20equity%20inflows%20dropped%20by%2022%25%20year-on-year%20to%20%2446%20billion%2C%20following%20a%201%25%20contraction%20from%20the%20previous%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20FDI%20equity%20inflow%20number%20looks%20slightly%20better%20when%20reinvested%20earnings%20and%20other%20forms%20of%20capital%20are%20taken%20into%20account%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fbusiness%2F2024%2FMar%2F26%2Fsluggish-fdi-growth-is-new-headache-for-govt%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENew%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022-23%2C%20the%20FDI%20growth%20declined%20by%2016%25%20to%20%2471%20billion%20compared%20to%20a%203%25%20increase%20to%20%2485%20billion%20in%20the%20previous%20year.%20In%20the%20current%20financial%20year%20till%20December%202023%2C%20the%20FDI%20in%20form%20of%20equity%20inflow%20was%2013%25%20lower%20y-o-y%20to%20%2432%20billion%2C%20the%20newspaper%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20finance%20ministry%20acknowledged%20this%20issue%2C%20attributing%20the%20dip%20in%20FDI%20inflows%20to%20a%20global%20slowdown%20and%20a%20rise%20in%20repatriation%20of%20investment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20slowdown%20in%20FDI%20growth%20is%20not%20a%20recent%20phenomenon.%20The%20slowdown%20has%20been%20setting%20in%20since%202016-17.%20In%20the%2010-year%20period%20to%202022-23%2C%20the%20FDI%20grew%20at%20a%20CAGR%20of%206.6%25%20compared%20to%2027%25%20in%20the%20previous%2010-year%20period.%20The%20FDI%20(equity%20inflow%2C%20reinvested%20earnings%20and%20other%20inflows%20put%20together)%20as%20a%20percentage%20of%20nominal%20GDP%20in%202022-23%20was%202.1%25%20compared%20to%202.7%25%20in%202021-22.%20The%20highest%20that%20India%20ever%20achieved%20was%203.5%25%20in%202008-09.%20In%20recent%20years%2C%202020-21%20saw%20India%E2%80%99s%20FDI%2FGDP%20ratio%20touching%203.1%25%20largely%20due%20to%20contraction%20in%20GDP%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBetween%20April%20and%20September%20of%20last%20year%2C%20India%20received%20a%20little%20over%20%2410%20billion%20in%20FDI%20%E2%80%93%20the%20lowest%20figure%20for%20the%20first%20half%20of%20a%20financial%20year%20since%20the%202008%20global%20recession%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthediplomat.com%2F2024%2F03%2Findia-suffering-a-quiet-decline-in-foreign-direct-investment%2F%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Feconomy%2Fwhy-fdi-in-india-is-lowest-in-16-yrs-no-real-ease-of-doing-business-ill-considered-treaty-moves%2F1927937%2F%5C%22%3ERBI.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnalysts%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Feconomy%2Fwhy-fdi-in-india-is-lowest-in-16-yrs-no-real-ease-of-doing-business-ill-considered-treaty-moves%2F1927937%2F%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Print%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20%E2%80%98rigidities%E2%80%99%20in%20doing%20business%20here%2C%20and%20India%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20terminate%20bilateral%20treaties%20are%20to%20blame.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20factors%20why%20foreign%20investment%20into%20India%20has%20been%20so%20tepid%20in%20recent%20years%20include%20bureaucratic%20red%20tape%2C%20a%20poor%20record%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Fopinion%2Fcontract-enforcement-key-to-ease-of-doing-business%2Farticle65238080.ece%5C%22%3Econtract%20enforcement%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20relatively%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2023%2F09%2F29%2Findias-labor-force-continues-to-lags-behind-chinas-study-.html%5C%22%3Elow%20labour%20productivity%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthediplomat.com%2F2024%2F03%2Findia-suffering-a-quiet-decline-in-foreign-direct-investment%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EDiplomat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20further%20attributes%20another%20factor%3A%20India%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20been%20signing%20enough%20deals%20to%20facilitate%20foreign%20investment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcfo.economictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fcorporate-finance%2Fwhy-are-indias-fdi-inflows-slowing-down%2F108662947%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EEconomic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20termination%20of%20numerous%20bilateral%20investment%20treaties%20and%20a%20shift%20towards%20protectionist%20trade%20policies%20have%20further%20dampened%20investor%20sentiment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEfforts%20to%20rectify%20these%20issues%20include%20recent%20trade%20agreements%20with%20Australia%2C%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%2C%20and%20the%20EFTA%20bloc.%20However%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20approach%20to%20negotiations%20remains%20cautious%2C%20with%20an%20emphasis%20on%20state%20control%20and%20limited%20exposure%20to%20foreign%20competition%2C%20said%20the%20business%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711456241000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F11%2F01171239%2Findian-rupee-money-cash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fred-tape-low-labour-productivity-protectionist-policies-slowing-down-indias-fdi-flow%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Between%20April%20and%20September%20of%20last%20year%2C%20India%20received%20a%20little%20over%20%2410%20billion%20in%20FDI%20%E2%80%93%20the%20lowest%20tally%20for%20the%20first%20half%20of%20a%20financial%20year%20since%20the%202008%20global%20recession%2C%20according%20to%20RBI.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fred-tape-low-labour-productivity-protectionist-policies-slowing-down-indias-fdi-flow%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Telangana%3A%20Why%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20Move%20to%20Appoint%20Chairs%20to%20State%20Entities%2C%20Form%20Caste%20Corporations%20Is%20Vital%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F29221132%2FEffect-4.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Telangana%20government%E2%80%99s%20move%20to%20appoint%20chairpersons%20to%2037%20corporations%2C%20or%20state-level%20entities%2C%20and%20other%20nominated%20posts%20was%20paused%20as%20the%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%20came%20into%20effect%20in%20the%20same%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20announced%20a%20list%20of%20selected%20chairpersons%20for%20the%2037%20entities%20on%20March%2016%2C%20the%20same%20day%20when%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Flok-sabha-election-schedule-2024-voting-to-start-on-april-19-counting-on-june-4%5C%22%3Eelection%20dates%20%3C%2Fa%3Efor%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20were%20announced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20the%20process%20was%20halted%20even%20before%20individual%20orders%20to%20each%20selected%20chairperson%20were%20issued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20yet%20another%20setback%2C%20albeit%20temporarily%2C%20to%20an%20ambitious%20programme%20of%20the%20Congress%20government%20which%20would%20have%20placed%20senior%20party%20leaders%2C%20who%20were%20denied%20poll%20tickets%2C%20in%20several%20caste-based%20corporations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%E2%80%99s%20programme%20to%20set%20up%20finance%20corporations%20for%2017%20caste%20groups%2C%20many%20of%20which%20belong%20to%20backward%20classes%2C%20also%20suffered%20a%20setback.%20These%20were%20in%20addition%20to%20the%2015%20other%20caste-based%20finance%20corporations%20already%20in%20existence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cabinet%20had%20announced%20the%20establishment%20of%2017%20corporations%20much%20earlier%20to%20the%20release%20of%20the%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20initiative%20is%20significant%20because%20this%20is%20the%20first%20time%20so%20many%20castes%20groups%20are%20getting%20finance%20corporations.%20Earlier%2C%20these%20castes%20used%20to%20get%20loans%20from%20umbrella%20organisations%20such%20as%20BC%20Corporation%20or%20SC%20Corporation.%20But%20now%2C%20individual%20castes%20have%20got%20their%20own%20finance%20corporations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20election%20code%20also%20brought%20to%20a%20standstill%20a%20caste%20survey%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fhyderabad%2Ftelangana-house-passes-resolution-on-caste-census%2Farticleshow%2F107764471.cms%5C%22%3Eproposed%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20be%20taken%20up%20in%20the%20state%20to%20identify%20the%20socioeconomic%20and%20educational%20standards%20of%20various%20sections.%20On%20February%2016%2C%20the%20government%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fhyderabad%2Ftelangana-house-passes-resolution-on-caste-census%2Farticleshow%2F107764471.cms%5C%22%3Epassed%20a%20resolution%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20caste%20census%20in%20the%20assembly%20and%20allotted%20Rs%20150%20crore%20for%20the%20purpose.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20significance%20of%20the%20initiatives%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20three%20initiatives%2C%20the%20appointment%20of%20chairpersons%20for%2037%20corporations%20was%20a%20significant%20move%20by%20the%20Congress%20government%20to%20reward%20its%20cadre%20after%20winning%20the%20assembly%20elections.%20Nominating%20individuals%20to%20these%20corporations%20serves%20as%20a%20crucial%20mechanism%20to%20rehabilitate%20middle%20and%20grassroots-level%20workers%20of%20any%20ruling%20party%20who%20could%20not%20contest%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20previous%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samiti%20(BRS)%20regime%20had%20neglected%20this%20issue%20and%20as%20a%20result%2C%20many%20of%20its%20cadres%20were%20disappointed.%20The%20BRS%20workers%E2%80%99%20frustration%20is%20evident%20through%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Felections%2Flok-sabha%2Findia%2Fblow-to-brs-in-telangana-sitting-mp-mla-resign-from-party-join-congress-ahead-of-ls-polls%2Farticleshow%2F108562044.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Eresignations%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Ftelangana%2Fstory%2Franjith-reddy-another-mp-kcrs-party-resigns-lok-sabha-polls-likely-join-congress-2515960-2024-03-17%5C%22%3Efrom%20the%20party.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20former%20chairman%2C%20who%20did%20not%20want%20to%20be%20named%2C%20said%20the%20BRS%20(then%20Telangana%20Rashtra%20Samithi)%20came%20to%20power%20in%202014%20but%20he%20got%20the%20post%20only%20in%202021%2C%20despite%20him%20being%20with%20the%20party%20since%20its%20inception%20in%202001.%20He%20said%20he%20had%20also%20spent%20considerable%20money%20from%20his%20pocket%20on%20the%20party%20programmes.%20He%20further%20said%20that%20only%20a%20handful%20of%20chairpersons%20like%20Gyadari%20Balamallu%20of%20Telangana%20State%20Industrial%20Infrastructure%20Corporation%20(TSIIC)%20survived%20in%20these%20posts%20for%20extended%20periods%20with%20the%20blessings%20of%20then%20chief%20minister%20K.%20Chandrashekar%20Rao.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBalamallu%20served%20the%20longest%20tenure%20in%20the%20post%20in%20the%20BRS%20government%2C%20holding%20it%20for%20seven%20years%20until%20his%20resignation%20after%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20defeat%20in%20the%20assembly%20polls.%20But%2C%20he%20was%20also%20appointed%20to%20TSIIC%20two%20years%20after%20the%20government%20was%20sworn%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20comparison%20to%20that%2C%20the%20Congress%20announced%20the%20appointments%20of%20its%20workers%20much%20earlier.%20It%20allocated%20the%20chairman%20post%20to%20lesser-known%20bodies%20such%20as%20Telangana%20State%20Oilseeds%20Growers%20Federation%2C%20Minimum%20Wages%20Advisory%20Board%20and%20Telangana%20Foods.%20The%20castes%20of%20the%20appointed%20persons%20were%20also%20disclosed%20in%20the%20list%20to%20ensure%20transparency%20in%20representation%20across%20all%20sections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20a%20cabinet%20meeting%2C%20chaired%20by%20chief%20minister%20A.%20Revanth%20Reddy%2C%20had%20sanctioned%20finance%20corporations%20to%2017%20caste%20groups%20belonging%20to%20backward%20classes%2C%20Scheduled%20Castes%2C%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20and%20forward%20castes%20like%20Reddy%2C%20Vaishya%20and%20Kamma.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20announcement%20of%20a%20special%20welfare%20board%20for%20the%20economically%20backward%20classes%20was%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20announcements%20were%20made%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20existing%20finance%20corporations%20and%20federations%20of%20cooperative%20societies%20for%20backward%20class%20communities%20identified%20by%20their%20trades%20like%20goldsmiths%2C%20potters%2C%20toddy%20tappers%2C%20washermen%2C%20barbers%2C%20construction%20workers%2C%20bead%20vendors%2C%20bamboo%20artisans%20and%20stone%20cutters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20corporation%20for%20backward%20classes%20and%20a%20separate%20one%20for%20the%20most%20backward%20classes%20(MBCs)%20existed%20even%20during%20the%20BRS%20government.%20However%2C%20it%20was%20confined%20to%20paper.%20The%20corporations%20lacked%20powers%20and%20funds.%20Even%20their%20staff%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20being%20paid%20salaries%20regularly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BRS%20government%20had%20started%20corporations%20for%20Muslim%20minorities%2C%20Christians%20and%20Brahmins%20beside%20SCs%20and%20STs%20but%20they%20too%20lacked%20adequate%20supervision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20assembly%20elections%2C%20the%20Congress%20had%20promised%20that%20it%20would%20set%20up%20finance%20corporations%20for%20all%20castes%20belonging%20to%20backward%20classes%20for%20their%20comprehensive%20development.%20It%20had%20also%20promised%20interest%20and%20security%20free%20loans%20of%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20for%20youngsters%20belonging%20to%20backward%20classes%20to%20start%20small%20trades.%20The%20promises%20were%20incorporated%20in%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20manifesto%20for%20the%20assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandrashekar%20Rao%20had%20often%20promised%20that%20his%20government%20would%20strengthen%20the%20corporation%20for%20MBCs%20with%20a%20Rs%201%2C000%20crore%20budget.%20However%2C%20these%20corporations%20hardly%20got%20anything%20from%20the%20BRS%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chairman%20of%20State%20Backward%20Classes%20Commission%20V.%20Krishna%20Mohan%20Rao%20said%20the%20demand%20for%20caste-based%20finance%20corporations%20was%20long-pending.%20The%20establishment%20of%20these%20corporations%20won%E2%80%99t%20make%20sense%20if%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t%20strive%20to%20extend%20economic%20support%20schemes%20that%20improved%20the%20living%20standards%20of%20the%20beneficiaries.%20He%20also%20suggested%20that%20the%20support%20should%20help%20people%20repay%20their%20loans%20and%20not%20come%20in%20the%20form%20of%20freebies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20BRS%20activist%20and%20a%20former%20member%20of%20State%20BC%20Commission%2C%20E.%20Anjaneya%20Goud%2C%20said%20the%20BC%20corporation%20was%20the%20funding%20agency%20for%20all%20cooperative%20societies%20under%20the%20BRS%20government.%20Emphasising%20on%20the%20significant%20impact%20these%20corporations%20had%2C%20he%20said%20that%20the%20cooperative%20societies%20for%20sheep%20rearing%20and%20fisheries%20in%20irrigation%20tanks%20generated%20huge%20wealth%20for%20village%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711454414000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F29221132%2FEffect-4.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-why-congresss-move-to-appoint-chairs-to-state-entities-form-caste-corporations-is-vital%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22These%20moves%2C%20including%20a%20caste%20survey%2C%20were%20halted%20due%20to%20the%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%20coming%20into%20force.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-why-congresss-move-to-appoint-chairs-to-state-entities-form-caste-corporations-is-vital%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Kisan%20Mazdoor%20Commission'%20to%20Look%20at%20Rising%20Challenges%20for%20Farmers%20in%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F26152957%2FScreenshot-2024-03-20-at-8.07.12%25E2%2580%25AFAM.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20the%20run%20up%20to%20the%20general%20elections%2C%20the%20Press%20Club%2C%20New%20Delhi%20recently%20witnessed%20the%20launching%20of%20new%20commission%20%E2%80%93%20Kisan%20Mazdoor%20Commission%20(KMC)%20%E2%80%93%20to%20address%20the%20overall%20structural%20problems%20in%20agriculture.%20The%20objective%20of%20the%20KMC%20is%20to%20go%20%E2%80%9Cbeyond%20the%20recommendations%20of%20Swaminathan%20Commission%20in%20the%20light%20of%20challenges%20arising%20out%20of%20the%20growing%20corporate%20control%20on%20the%20supply%20of%20farm%20inputs%20resulting%20in%20the%20rising%20cost%20of%20production%20for%20farmers%20and%20on%20the%20markets%20for%20agricultural%20produce%20leading%20to%20the%20loss%20of%20incomes%20from%20farming%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20commission%20came%20out%20of%20discussions%20held%20between%20experts%2C%20farmers%2C%20labour%20unions%20and%20farm%20workers%E2%80%99%20unions%20under%20the%20banner%20of%20%E2%80%98Nation%20for%20Farmers%E2%80%99%20and%20later%20morphed%20into%20KMC.%20This%20commission%2C%20unlike%20others%2C%20aims%20to%20bring%20workers%20and%20farmers%20themselves%20into%20the%20agro-policy%20discussions.%20Jagmohan%20Singh%20has%20been%20voted%20as%20the%20national%20convenor%2C%20while%20Vijoo%20Krishnan%2C%20Navsharan%20Kaur%2C%20Roma%20Malik%2C%20Dinesh%20Abrol%2C%20P.%20Sainath%2C%20Thomas%20Franco%20and%20Nikhil%20Dey%20will%20be%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20KMC%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Agenda%20for%202024%E2%80%99%20aims%20to%20study%20%E2%80%9Crising%20cost%20of%20production%2C%20income%20enhancement%2C%20trade%20and%20investment%20(WTO%20and%20FTAs)%2C%20rural%20credit%20and%20insurance%2C%20common%20pool%20resources%2C%20ecological%20challenge%2C%20food%20and%20nutrition%2C%20women%20farmers%20and%20rural%20non-farm%20enterprises%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20senior%20journalist%20and%20Ramon%20Magsaysay%20awardee%20Sainath%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CM.S.%20Swaminathan%E2%80%99s%20life%E2%80%99s%20greatest%20contribution%20(the%20Swaminathan%20report%20on%20MSP)%20is%20ridiculed%20and%20thrown%20out%2C%20and%20meanwhile%20he%20was%20given%20a%20Bharat%20Ratna.%20We%20also%20become%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20first%20country%20to%20use%20aerial%20drone%20warfare%20against%20farmers.%20We%20didn%E2%80%99t%20use%20this%20against%20the%20terrorist%20but%20against%20the%20farmers.%20Drones%20dropped%20tear%20gas%20canisters%20on%20peacefully%20protesting%20farmers.%20%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20on%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20response%20to%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20movement%2C%20Sainath%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20package%20they%20(the%20Union%20government)%20offered%20was%20farm%20laws%20through%20the%20back%20door%2C%20it%20said%20we%20will%20expand%20MSP%20to%20five%20crops%2C%20but%20on%20paper%20it%E2%80%99s%2023%20crops%20already%20%E2%80%93%20if%20you%20go%20to%20five%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20reduction.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20if%20we%20look%20at%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20own%20household%20consumption%20survey%2C%20whose%20veracity%20I%20doubt%2C%20even%20those%20figures%20show%20us%20that%20farmers%E2%80%99%20incomes%20are%20lower%20than%20the%20rural%20average.%20That%20is%20why%20KMC%20its%20a%20platform%20with%20farmers%20and%20mazdoors%20in%20the%20forefront%2C%20I%20too%20am%20only%20member%20of%20the%20drafting%20committee.%20It%20is%20time%20to%20update%20and%20go%20beyond%20the%20Swaminathan%20Commission%20to%20address%20newer%20challenges%20like%20climate%20change%2C%20etc.%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20issues%20the%20KMC%20proposes%20to%20look%20into%20are%20the%20Electricity%20Amendment%20Act%2C%20policy%20on%20water%20which%20is%20a%20basic%20right%2C%20pension%20scheme%2C%20Forest%20Rights%20Act%20implementation%2C%20MGNREGA%20implementation%2C%20policies%20on%20fisheries%2C%20rain%20fed%20dry%20land%20agriculture%2C%20climate%20crisis%2C%20biodiversity%20loss%20and%20seed%20systems.%20The%20KMC%20is%20planning%20to%20hold%20special%20consultations%20on%20the%20subjects%20of%20land%20rights%20for%20women%20farmers%20including%20women%20agricultural%20workers%2C%20rights%20of%20rural%20labour%20which%20will%20include%20all%20the%20basic%20rights%20(not%20just%20wages%20but%20access%20to%20capabilities%20and%20markets)%2C%20and%20the%20connections%20between%20agrarian%20crisis%2C%20environmental%20degradation%20and%20climate%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENavsharan%20Kaur%20whose%20is%20leading%20the%20research%20on%20women%20within%20the%20KMC%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CWomen%20are%20highly%20disadvantaged%20in%20agriculture.%20Despite%20being%20about%2060%25%20of%20the%20workforce%2C%20women%20barely%20own%20any%20land%20and%20in%20most%20places%20are%20not%20even%20counted%20as%20farmers.%20Even%20when%20we%20look%20the%20PM%20Kisan%20scheme%2C%20it%20hardly%20has%20any%20women%20beneficiaries.%20Women%20hardly%20have%20access%20to%20resources%20in%20agriculture.%20KMC%20will%20attempt%20to%20bridge%20this%20inequality.%20Apart%20from%20getting%20women%E2%80%99s%20needs%20to%20the%20forefront%2C%20we%20hope%20to%20influence%20policy%20through%20which%20women%20get%20more%20access%20to%20land%20in%20the%20villages%20and%20to%20create%20food%20and%20vegetables%20areas%20for%20better%20nutrition.%20Unused%20land%20within%20the%20public%20sector%2C%20should%20be%20redistributed%20to%20poor%20and%20landless%20women%20instead%20of%20corporates.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKMC%20has%20also%20set%20up%20other%20working%20groups%20to%20tackle%20the%20issues%20of%20%E2%80%9CAnalysis%20of%20Cost%20of%20Production%20and%20Income%20Sources%3B%20Analysis%20of%20Public%20%26amp%3B%20Private%20Investments%3B%20Farming%20Systems%3B%20Agricultural%20R%20%26amp%3B%20D%3B%20Agri-Digitalization%3B%20Rural%20Labour%3B%20Nutrition%20%26amp%3B%20Food%20Safety%3B%20Commons%3B%20Trade%20%26amp%3B%20Investment%3B%20Credit%20%26amp%3B%20Insurance.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDinesh%20Abrol%20also%20addressed%20the%20press%20conference%20and%20spoke%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%20He%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20root%20cause%20of%20the%20agrarian%20crisis%20is%20the%20capture%20of%20public%20sector%20institutions%20by%20domestic%20and%20foreign%20corporations%2C%20for%20example%20Amazon%2C%20a%20retailing%20company%2C%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fretail.economictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fe-commerce%2Fe-tailing%2Famazon-signs-pact-with-icar-to-empower-farmers-enrolled-under-kisan-store%2F100889478%5C%22%3Enow%20working%20with%3C%2Fa%3E%20Ministry%20of%20Agriculture%20on%20agriculture%20extension.%20How%20does%20this%20happen%3F%20Corporatisation%20of%20agriculture%20is%20happening%20at%20a%20very%20rapid%20pace.%20My%20own%20research%20on%20the%20Green%20Revolution%20shows%20this%2C%20because%20instead%20of%20scientific%20management%20and%20use%20of%20agri-inputs%2C%20now%20companies%20are%20pushing%20more%20chemicals%20and%20inputs%20to%20boost%20their%20business.%20This%20is%20huge%20cost%20for%20the%20farmers%20and%20ecology%20of%20the%20country.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711451700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F26152957%2FScreenshot-2024-03-20-at-8.07.12%25E2%2580%25AFAM.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fkisan-mazdoor-commission-to-look-at-rising-challenges-for-farmers-in-india%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20objective%20of%20the%20KMC%20is%20to%20go%20%E2%80%9Cbeyond%20the%20recommendations%20of%20Swaminathan%20Commission%20in%20the%20light%20of%20challenges%20arising%20out%20of%20the%20growing%20corporate%20control%20on%20the%20supply%20of%20farm%20inputs%20resulting%20in%20the%20rising%20cost%20of%20production%20for%20farmers%20and%20on%20the%20markets%20for%20agricultural%20produce%20leading%20to%20the%20loss%20of%20incomes%20from%20farming%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fkisan-mazdoor-commission-to-look-at-rising-challenges-for-farmers-in-india%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Government%E2%80%99s%20Claims%20on%20Poverty%20Reduction%20Are%20False.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20Why.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F28104109%2F1339849094_15ec84bbc4_c.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chief%20executive%20officer%20of%20Niti%20Aayog%20made%20a%20fantastic%20claim%20that%20the%20poverty%20ratio%20in%20India%20had%20fallen%20below%205%25%20according%20to%20the%202022-23%20consumption%20expenditure%20survey%20data.%20His%20claim%20was%20based%20on%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20per%20capita%20consumption%20expenditures%20of%20only%205%25%20of%20the%20population%20in%202022-23%20fell%20below%20the%20poverty-lines%20for%20that%20year%20for%20rural%20and%20urban%20India%2C%20arrived%20at%20by%20updating%2C%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20consumer%20price%20indices%2C%20the%20poverty-lines%20suggested%20for%202011-12%20by%20a%20committee%20headed%20by%20Suresh%20Tendulkar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20the%20Tendulkar%20committee%20had%20not%20based%20its%202011-12%20poverty%20lines%20on%20any%20objective%20criteria%2C%20such%20as%20minimum%20calorie%20intake%2C%20or%20the%20price%20of%20a%20minimum%20necessary%20basket%20of%20goods%3B%20it%20had%20simply%20made%20some%20arbitrary%20decisions%20regarding%20what%20these%20lines%20should%20be.%20Besides%2C%20the%20consumer%20price%20indices%20being%20used%20for%20updating%20these%20Tendulkar%20poverty%20lines%20have%20serious%20underestimation%20biases%20as%20they%20do%20not%20take%20adequate%20account%20of%20the%20privatisation%20of%20essential%20services%20like%20education%20and%20healthcare.%20Moreover%20the%20consumption%20expenditure%20survey%20for%202022-23%20has%20been%20conducted%20on%20different%20lines%20from%20all%20earlier%20surveys%20because%20of%20which%20its%20results%20are%20not%20comparable%20with%20earlier%20results%2C%20and%20its%20biases%20are%20not%20yet%20fully%20known%20because%20the%20complete%20data%20has%20not%20been%20released.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%205%25%20claim%20made%20by%20the%20Niti%20Aayog%2C%20therefore%2C%20has%20little%20sanctity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20it%20flies%20in%20the%20face%20of%20a%20mass%20of%20other%20information%20that%20we%20have%20about%20the%20economy%2C%20because%20of%20which%20the%20conclusion%20is%20inescapable%20that%20this%20figure%20is%20being%20pushed%20by%20the%20government%20for%20propaganda%20purposes%20before%20the%20elections.%20Let%20us%20see%20what%20this%20other%20information%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20findings%20of%20the%202017-18%20consumption%20expenditure%20survey%20were%20so%20abysmal%20that%20they%20were%20withdrawn%20by%20the%20government.%20But%20from%20whatever%20was%20leaked%20out%2C%20it%20could%20be%20calculated%20that%20the%20proportion%20of%20persons%20in%20urban%20India%20who%20could%20not%20access%202100%20calories%20per%20person%20per%20day%2C%20the%20original%20Planning%20Commission%20benchmark%20for%20urban%20poverty%2C%20was%20as%20high%20as%2060%25.%20This%20is%20higher%20than%2057%25%20for%201993-94%2C%20though%20lower%20than%2065%25%20for%202011-12.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20rural%20India%2C%20however%2C%20the%20proportion%20that%20could%20not%20access%202200%20calories%20per%20person%20per%20day%2C%20the%20corresponding%20benchmark%2C%20was%20well%20over%2080%25%20in%202017-2018%2C%20compared%20to%2058%25%20in%201993-94%20and%2068%25%20in%202011-12.%20Taking%20the%20two%20together%2C%20clearly%20the%20true%20poverty%20ratio%20in%202017-18%20was%20significantly%20higher%20than%20in%202011-12%20given%20the%20much%20higher%20weight%20of%20rural%20India%20in%20the%20total.%20(These%20figures%20are%20from%20Utsa%20Patnaik%E2%80%99s%20forthcoming%20book.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fthe-truth-behind-the-governments-claim-that-poverty-has-fallen-to-just-5%5C%22%3EThe%20Truth%20Behind%20the%20Government%E2%80%99s%20Claim%20That%20Poverty%20Has%20Fallen%20to%20Just%205%25%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPoverty%2C%20in%20short%2C%20had%20increased%20significantly%20between%202011-12%20and%202017-18.%20After%202017-18%20we%20have%20had%20a%20pandemic%2C%20and%20a%20lockdown%20induced%20by%20it%2C%20from%20which%20the%20economy%20is%20just%20recovering%2C%20although%20unemployment%20today%20is%20higher%20than%20before%20the%20pandemic.%20The%20claim%20that%20the%20poverty%20ratio%20has%20come%20down%20compared%20to%202011-12%2C%20whence%20it%20would%20follow%20that%20it%20has%20come%20down%20even%20more%20sharply%20compared%20to%202017-18%2C%20precisely%20in%20a%20period%20when%20the%20economy%20was%20racked%20by%20a%20pandemic%2C%20defies%20credibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20course%20it%20would%20be%20argued%20that%20calorie%20intake%20cannot%20be%20an%20indicator%20of%20poverty.%20But%20this%20argument%20is%20based%20on%20a%20misunderstanding.%20The%20point%20is%20not%20that%20calorie%20intake%C2%A0%3Cem%3Ealone%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Eshould%20count%20for%20estimating%20poverty%3B%20the%20point%20is%20that%20whenever%20there%20is%20an%20increase%20in%20real%20income%2C%20it%20necessarily%20also%20shows%20itself%20in%20terms%20of%20an%20increase%20in%20calorie%20intake.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20the%20proposition%20that%20there%20could%20be%20a%20reduction%20in%20calorie%20intake%20even%20when%20a%20person%20becomes%20better%20off%2C%20at%20levels%20of%20intake%20that%20one%20finds%20in%20countries%20like%20ours%2C%20is%20wholly%20untenable.%20If%20it%20occurs%20then%20that%20must%20be%20treated%20as%20a%20worsening%20of%20real%20income.%20And%20empirical%20evidence%20fully%20supports%20this%20proposition%20that%20there%20is%20a%20clear%20positive%20relationship%20between%20per%20capita%20income%20and%20per%20capita%20cereal%20consumption%20(which%20also%20means%20per%20capita%20calorie%20intake).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20there%20are%20no%20data%20on%20incomes%20whatsoever%2C%20and%20since%20consumption%20expenditure%20data%20which%20are%20available%20can%20be%20meaningfully%20compared%20across%20time%20only%20by%20using%20some%20price%20index%20and%20all%20such%20indices%20are%20unreliable%2C%20taking%20calorie%20intake%20as%20a%20proxy%20for%20real%20income%20and%20comparing%20such%20intake%20over%20time%20makes%20perfect%20sense.%20And%20if%20we%20do%20so%2C%20then%20until%202017-18%2C%20the%20poverty%20ratio%20in%20the%20country%20had%20increased%20and%20after%20that%20we%20simply%20do%20not%20know.%20If%20the%20government%20makes%20available%20the%20calorie%20intake%20information%20contained%20in%20the%20consumption%20survey%20for%202022-23%2C%20which%20it%20has%20not%20yet%20done%2C%20then%20we%20shall%20know%20for%20sure%20what%20has%20been%20happening%20to%20poverty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUntil%20then%2C%20however%2C%20we%20can%20only%20fall%20back%20on%20stray%20indirect%20evidence%20and%20virtually%20all%20such%20evidence%20points%20not%20just%20to%20the%20existence%20of%20substantial%20poverty%20in%20the%20country%20but%20even%20to%20an%20increase%20rather%20than%20a%20decrease%20in%20the%20poverty%20ratio.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20such%20indirect%20evidence%20is%20from%20the%20National%20Family%20Health%20Survey.%20The%20NFHS-5%2C%20covering%202019-21%2C%20shows%20that%20the%20incidence%20of%20anaemia%20among%20women%20in%20the%20age-group%2015-49%20has%20increased%20compared%20to%20NFHS-4%20(2015-16)%2C%20with%2057%25%20being%20anaemic%20on%20the%20later%20date%20compared%20to%2053%25%20earlier.%20The%20number%20of%20states%20where%20more%20than%20half%20the%20women%20were%20anaemic%20was%2025%20in%202019-21%20compared%20to%2021%20in%202015-16.%20It%20is%20often%20argued%20that%20the%20incidence%20of%20anaemia%20among%20Indian%20women%20is%20overstated%20because%20the%20same%20criteria%20which%20are%20used%20in%20the%20west%20are%20also%20applied%20in%20India%2C%20which%20is%20incorrect.%20But%20this%20argument%2C%20even%20if%20one%20accepts%20it%20for%20a%20particular%20point%20of%20time%2C%20does%20not%20apply%20to%20comparisons%20over%20time%3B%20the%20worsening%20in%20this%20respect%20over%20time%20therefore%20is%20quite%20indubitable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20bit%20of%20indirect%20evidence%20comes%20from%20the%20global%20hunger%20index.%20In%202023%2C%20India%20occupied%20the%20111th%20position%20among%20the%20125%20countries%20for%20whom%20the%20GHI%20is%20calculated.%20The%20government%20of%20India%20has%20objected%20to%20the%20index%20stating%20that%20it%20is%20a%20flawed%20measure.%20But%20no%20matter%20whether%20one%20agrees%20with%20the%20variables%20that%20are%20included%20in%20the%20hunger%20index%20and%20the%20weights%20given%20to%20these%20variables%2C%20a%20country%20that%20witnesses%20a%20significant%20increase%20in%20the%20per%20capita%20real%20income%20even%20for%20the%20bottom%20deciles%20of%20the%20population%2C%20which%20alone%20can%20explain%20the%20claimed%20sharp%20decline%20in%20poverty%2C%20should%20certainly%20be%20seeing%20an%20improvement%20in%20its%20position%20in%20the%20hunger%20index.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20is%20not%20all.%20On%20most%20of%20the%20variables%20included%20in%20the%20computation%20of%20the%20hunger%20index%2C%20namely%20population%20undernourishment%2C%20child%20wasting%2C%20child%20stunting%2C%20and%20child%20mortality%2C%20the%20situation%20in%202023%20was%20distinctly%20worse%20than%20in%202008%3B%20the%20only%20exception%20was%20in%20undernourishment%2C%20where%20it%20was%20roughly%20the%20same%20but%20distinctly%20worse%20than%20in%202000.%20True%2C%20those%20who%20prepare%20the%20hunger%20index%20warn%20that%20scores%20across%20time%20should%20not%20be%20compared%2C%20strictly%20speaking%2C%20because%20of%20changes%20in%20data%20source%3B%20nonetheless%2C%20the%20fact%20that%20there%20has%20been%20a%20worsening%20in%20all%20indicators%20that%20go%20into%20the%20hunger%20index%2C%20compared%20to%202008%20or%202000%2C%20clearly%20suggests%20that%20the%20claimed%20improvement%20in%20the%20real%20incomes%20of%20the%20bottom%20deciles%20of%20the%20population%20(which%20alone%20would%20explain%20the%20sharp%20decline%20in%20poverty)%20has%20no%20basis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20bit%20of%20indirect%20evidence%20comes%20from%20the%20so-called%20%E2%80%9Czero%20food%20children%E2%80%9D%2C%20that%20is%20children%20between%206%20and%2023%20months%20who%20have%20not%20had%20any%20food%20other%20than%20breast%20milk%20in%20the%20previous%2024%20hours.%20%E2%80%9CZero%20food%E2%80%9D%20of%20course%20gives%20the%20impression%20that%20such%20children%20have%20had%20no%C2%A0%3Cem%3Efood%20at%20all%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0which%20is%20incorrect%3B%20what%20it%20actually%20means%20is%20that%20they%20have%20had%20no%20supplementary%20food%20apart%20from%20breast%20milk%20in%20the%20previous%2024%20hours.%20And%20there%20were%206.7%20million%20such%20children%20in%20India%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fact%20that%20this%20is%20a%20deprivation%20is%20undeniable%3B%20and%20even%20though%20the%20reason%20may%20not%20always%20have%20to%20do%20with%20the%20absence%20of%20purchasing%20power%20with%20the%20family%2C%20it%20certainly%20is%20linked%20to%20parents%20having%20to%20work%20long%20hours%20for%20their%20livelihood%2C%20which%20is%20just%20another%20manifestation%20of%20poverty.%20The%20percentage%20of%20such%20children%20within%20the%20total%20number%20of%20children%20in%20the%20relevant%20age-group%20comes%20to%2019.3%25%20in%20India%20%E2%80%93%20the%20third%20highest%20among%20all%20the%20countries%20of%20the%20world%20after%20Guinea%20(21.8%25)%20and%20Mali%20(20.5%20%25).%20This%20also%20suggests%20that%20the%20claimed%20increase%20in%20real%20income%2C%20which%20is%20supposed%20to%20have%20banished%20poverty%20from%20the%20land%2C%20is%20completely%20unfounded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20matter%20what%20spin%20the%20government%20gives%20on%20poverty%20the%20world%20knows%20that%20India%20is%20a%20desperately%20poor%20country.%20A%20recent%20UN%20report%20has%20found%20that%20as%20much%20as%2074%25%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20population%20cannot%20afford%20the%20minimum%20nutritious%20diet%20that%20is%20prescribed%20by%20the%20FAO%20for%20South%20Asia%3B%20this%20is%20a%20shocking%20fact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20published%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpeoplesdemocracy.in%2F2024%2F0324_pd%2Fonce-more-poverty-figures-india%5C%22%3EPeople%E2%80%99s%20Democracy.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EPrabhat%20Patnaik%20is%20professor%20emeritus%20of%20economics%20at%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711450208000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F28104109%2F1339849094_15ec84bbc4_c.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fthe-governments-claims-of-poverty-reduction-are-false-heres-why%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Niti%20Aayog's%20claim%20that%20poverty%20has%20fallen%20to%205%25%20flies%20in%20the%20face%20of%20a%20mass%20of%20other%20information%20that%20we%20have%20about%20the%20economy%2C%20because%20of%20which%20the%20conclusion%20is%20inescapable%20that%20this%20figure%20is%20being%20pushed%20by%20the%20government%20for%20propaganda%20purposes%20before%20the%20elections.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fthe-governments-claims-of-poverty-reduction-are-false-heres-why%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bananas%2C%20Umbrellas%20and%20Other%20Evidence%3A%20The%20Astounding%20Case%20of%20G.N.%20Saibaba's%20Trial%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F07181050%2Fimage-1914.png%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Nagpur%20bench%20of%20the%20Bombay%20high%20court%20heard%20the%20appeal%20against%20the%20conviction%20of%20%C2%A0and%20five%20others%2C%20twice.%20In%20both%20the%20judgments%2C%20it%20set%20aside%20the%20conviction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hearing%20was%20held%20in%20a%20fully%20packed%20courtroom%20with%2C%20at%20times%2C%20hot-tempered%20exchanges%20of%20strong%20arguments.%20Needless%20to%20say%20the%20atmosphere%20was%20terribly%20tense.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20one%20proposition%20of%20Pradip%20Mandhyan%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20so%20hilarious%E2%80%94%20although%20hard-hitting%E2%80%94%20that%20the%20entire%20courtroom%20would%20burst%20into%20laughter%20every%20time%20it%20was%20mentioned.%20He%20pointed%20out%20that%20one%20of%20the%20most%20incriminating%20items%20was%20missing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20missing%20article%20was%20a%20banana.%20Yes%2C%20a%20banana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ten-year-long%20ordeal%20of%20the%20six%20%E2%80%98Urban%20Naxals%E2%80%99%20ended%20on%20March%205%2C%202024.%20Pronouncing%20the%20judgment%20in%20the%20court%20full%20of%20lawyers%20and%20journalists%2C%20the%20otherwise%20calm%20and%20soft-spoken%20Justice%20Vinay%20G.%20Joshi%20seemed%20to%20be%20in%20a%20totally%20different%20mood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20voice%20firm%2C%20resolute%2C%20determined%20and%20unusually%20loud%2C%20conveyed%20that%20they%20were%20delivering%20well-deserved%20justice%20by%20overturning%20the%20conviction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimply%20put%2C%20the%20judgment%20said%20what%20we%20lawyers%20often%20say%3A%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20nothing%20in%20the%20matter%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENothing%20worth%20a%20conviction%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20nothing%20worthy%20even%20of%20a%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ECharges%20%E2%80%98serious%E2%80%99%20enough%20to%20be%20hospitalised%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20conviction%20by%20the%20trial%20court%20had%20come%20as%20a%20surprise%20to%20everyone%2C%20except%20the%20police.%20The%20case%20was%20made%20sensational%20right%20from%20the%20first%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20first%20round%20of%20hearings%20in%20appeal%20before%20the%20high%20court%20went%20mostly%20unnoticed%20by%20the%20national%20media%2C%20its%20%3Ca%20data-wpel-link%3D%5C%22internal%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheleaflet.in%2Fbombay-high-court-acquits-ex-du-professor-saibaba-in-maoist-links-case%2F%5C%22%3Ejudgment%3C%2Fa%3E%20created%20uproar.%20Even%20before%20the%20ink%20could%20dry%2C%20the%20State%20went%20in%20appeal%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20the%20very%20same%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20then%20to-be%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%2C%20Dr%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%2C%20refused%20an%20urgent%20listing.%20However%2C%20within%20a%20short%20time%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20convened%20a%20special%20Bench%20on%20a%20Saturday%20morning%20to%20hear%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20specially%20constituted%20Bench%20consisting%20of%20Justices%20M.R.%20Shah%20and%20Bela%20Trivedi%20gave%20an%20unprecedented%20%3Ca%20data-wpel-link%3D%5C%22internal%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheleaflet.in%2Fsupreme-court-stays-bombay-high-courts-order-discharging-former-du-professor-saibaba-delays-his-freedom%2F%5C%22%3Estay%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20acquittal.%20Additionally%2C%20it%20refused%20to%20grant%20medical%20bail%20or%20even%20house%20arrest%20to%20the%20ailing%2C%2090%25%20disabled%2C%20wheelchair-bound%20professor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20was%20otherwise%20a%20one-sided%20case%20was%20turned%20into%20a%20highly%20contested%20one%20by%20the%20State%2C%20as%20it%20fielded%20some%20of%20its%20best%20pleaders.%20The%20best%20of%20lawyers%20advanced%20some%20of%20the%20most%20novel%20technical%20arguments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBail%20applications%20were%20opposed%20tooth%20and%20nail.%20Although%20all%20six%20appellants%20were%20on%20bail%20during%20the%20trial%2C%20their%20bail%2C%20pending%20the%20appeal%2C%20was%20rejected.%20In%20one%20of%20the%20hearings%2C%20the%20special%20prosecutor%20even%20admitted%2C%20on%20record%2C%20that%20there%20is%20no%20act%20of%20terrorism%2C%20attributed%2C%20proved%20or%20alleged%20against%20any%20of%20these%20persons%2C%20yet%20bail%20was%20rejected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Saibaba%20applied%20for%20parole%20to%20visit%20his%20ailing%20mother%2C%20even%20that%20was%20rejected.%20The%20charges%20were%20%E2%80%98serious%E2%80%99%3B%20the%20love%20of%20a%20son%20for%20his%20mother%20could%20wait.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20seven%20years%2C%20at%20least%20four%20special%20prosecutors%20were%20appointed.%20When%20the%20bail%20application%20of%20Professor%20Saibaba%20was%20about%20to%20be%20moved%2C%20his%20lawyer%20Surendra%20Gadling%20was%20arrested%20and%20booked%20under%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22external%20noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiacode.nic.in%2Fhandle%2F123456789%2F1470%5C%22%20data-wpel-link%3D%5C%22external%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUnlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%2C%201967%3C%2Fa%3E%20(UAPA)%20in%20the%20infamous%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fbhima-koregaon-16-must-not-be-forgotten%5C%22%3EBhima%20Koregaon%E2%80%93Elgar%20Parishad%20case%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20has%20been%20in%20jail%20ever%20since.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20every%20hearing%2C%20high-rank%20police%20officers%20would%20sit%20in%20the%20courtroom.%20In%20the%20first%20round%2C%20when%20the%20investigating%20officer%20was%20not%20satisfied%20with%20the%20arguments%20made%20by%20the%20senior%20counsel%20appearing%20for%20the%20State%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20make%20some%20arguments%20himself%20to%20explain%20how%20%E2%80%9CUrban%20Naxals%E2%80%9D%20operate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20court%20asked%20a%20very%20basic%20question%20at%20the%20outset%2C%20he%20was%20left%20speechless%2C%20and%20then%20quietly%20vanished%20from%20the%20courtroom%20during%20the%20lunch%20break.%20In%20the%20second%20round%2C%20the%20State%20changed%20the%20special%20counsel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20both%20rounds%20of%20appeal%20that%20took%20place%20in%20the%20high%20court%2C%20of%20the%20various%20points%20argued%2C%20one%20of%20the%20major%20contentions%20was%20that%20of%20%E2%80%9Cbias%20of%20the%20trial%20judge%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssailing%20the%20judgment%20of%20the%20trial%20court%2C%20advocate%20Pradip%20Mandhyan%20would%20strenuously%20call%20it%20the%20outcome%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Cperverse%2C%20corrupt%20and%20dishonest%E2%80%9D%20act%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20presiding%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20all%20the%20reasons%20to%20say%20so.%20Apart%20from%20what%20has%20been%20held%20in%20the%20judgment%20of%20the%20high%20court%20on%20the%20nature%20of%20evidence%2C%20a%20few%20facts%20would%20reveal%20the%20real%20basis%20of%20this%20argument.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch4%3E%3Cb%3EA%201%2C000%20pages%20of%20perversity%2C%20corruption%20and%20dishonesty%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh4%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judgment%20rendered%20by%20the%20trial%20court%2C%20which%20can%20even%20be%20seen%20on%20various%20online%20platforms%2C%20runs%20into%20about%20a%20thousand%20pages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20holding%20all%20six%20persons%20guilty%2C%20in%20Paragraph%201%2C013%2C%20the%20learned%20sessions%20judge%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9C%5BI%5Dn%20my%20opinion%2C%20the%20imprisonment%20for%20life%20is%20also%20not%20a%20sufficient%20punishment%20to%20the%20accused%20but%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20court%20are%20closed%20with%20the%20mandate%20of%20Section%2018%20and%2020%20of%20UAPA%20and%20in%20my%20opinion%20it%20is%20a%20fit%20case%20to%20award%20sentence%20of%20life%20imprisonment%20to%20accused.%E2%80%9D%20(sic).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeaning%20thereby%2C%20that%20the%20court%20wanted%20to%20sentence%20them%20to%20death%2C%20but%20its%20hands%20were%20closed%20(tied)%20for%20the%20law%20did%20not%20provide%20for%20such%20punishment%20under%20the%20invoked%20provision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20timeline%20of%20the%20case%2C%20if%20seen%2C%20will%20bear%20out%20that%20the%20statements%20of%20the%20accused%20under%20Section%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22external%20noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiacode.nic.in%2Fshow-data%3Factid%3DAC_CEN_5_23_000010_197402_1517807320555%26orderno%3D355%5C%22%20data-wpel-link%3D%5C%22external%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E313%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20Code%20of%20Criminal%20Procedure%20were%20recorded%20well%20up%20to%20January%209%2C%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThereafter%2C%20oral%20submissions%20by%20the%20counsels%20began%2C%20which%20stretched%20for%20about%20a%20month.%20Ultimately%20on%20February%209%2C%202017%2C%20the%20defence%20filed%20its%20written%20note%2C%20and%20the%20matter%20was%20reserved%20for%20judgment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20weeks%20later%2C%20i.e.%2C%20on%20February%2028%2C%202017%2C%20the%20matter%20again%20appeared%20on%20the%20board%2C%20for%20the%20prosecution%20wanted%20to%20cite%20some%20judgments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20less%20than%20a%20month%20since%20reserving%20the%20judgment%2C%20at%201%20p.m.%20on%20March%207%2C%202017%2C%20the%20sessions%20court%20at%20Gadchiroli%20pronounced%20the%20judgment%20running%20into%20827%20pages%2C%20holding%20all%20six%20guilty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20six%20were%20called%20upon%20to%20make%20submissions%20on%20sentences%20to%20be%20awarded.%20The%20defence%20counsel%2C%20Surendra%20Gadling%2C%20refused%20to%20make%20any%20submissions.%20Prashant%20Rahi%2C%20Hem%20Mishra%2C%20Vijay%20Nan%20Tirki%20and%20Saibaba%20also%20refused%20to%20make%20any%20submissions.%20No%20one%20believed%20that%20this%20was%20a%20case%20where%20a%20conviction%20could%20have%20been%20given.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%203%20p.m.%20on%20the%20same%20day%2C%20the%20learned%20judge%20pronounced%20the%20sentence%20of%20life%20to%20five%20and%2010%20years%20to%20Vijay%2C%20with%20reasons%20running%20into%2014%20pages.%20Each%20one%20of%20them%20was%20handed%20over%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20judgment%20right%20then%20and%20there%2C%20i.e.%2C%20prints%20of%20about%205%2C000%20pages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERendering%20such%20a%20bulky%20judgment%20in%20less%20than%2030%20days%20is%20not%20impossible.%20It%20can%20be%20done%2C%20of%20course.%20But%20that%20alone%20need%20not%20raise%20eyebrows.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%2C%20in%20the%20first%20round%20of%20appeal%2C%20the%20high%20court%20took%20about%2015%20days%20to%20render%20its%20judgment%20of%20about%20100%20pages%20restricted%20to%20the%20issue%20of%20sanction%2C%20while%20in%20the%20second%20round%2C%20it%20took%20nearly%20175%20days%20to%20render%20a%20293-page%20verdict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trial%20court%20felt%20life%20imprisonment%20was%20not%20sufficient%20because%20it%20blamed%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(CPI)%20(Maoist)%20and%20the%20Maoist%20movement%20in%20India%20for%20the%20non-industrialisation%20of%20the%20Gadchiroli%20district%20in%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trial%20court%20held%2C%20%E2%80%9CGadchiroli%20district%20today%20is%20same%20as%20it%20was%20in%20the%20year%201982%20and%20for%20that%20the%20accused%20no.%201%20to%206%20and%20members%20of%20banned%20organisation%20CPI%20(Maoist)%20and%20its%20frontal%20organisation%20Revolutionary%20Democratic%20Front%20(RDF)%20are%20responsible.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fit-is-only-by-chance-that-i-came-out-of-prison-alive-g-n-saibaba%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98It%20Is%20Only%20by%20Chance%20That%20I%20Came%20Out%20of%20Prison%20Alive%E2%80%99%3A%20G.N.%20Saibaba%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20gave%20various%20statistics%20that%20were%20never%20cited%20at%20the%20Bar%20and%20the%20source%20of%20which%20is%20mentioned%20to%20be%20%E2%80%9Cgovernment%20records%E2%80%9D.%20The%20trial%20court%20held%20that%20Professor%20Saibaba%2C%20though%2090%25%20disabled%2C%20is%20mentally%20fit%2C%20and%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9Cthink%20tank%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Chigh-profile%20leader%E2%80%9D%20of%20CPI%20(Maoist).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20draw%20these%20conclusions%20and%20not%20give%20a%20death%20sentence%2C%20the%20judge%20accepted%20the%20case%20of%20the%20prosecution%2C%20not%20just%20in%20its%20entirety%2C%20but%20even%20over%20and%20beyond%20what%20it%20was.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trial%20court%20referred%20to%20material%20that%20none%20of%20the%20prosecution%20witnesses%20had%20even%20uttered%20in%20their%20depositions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20hoard%20of%20material%20that%20was%20%E2%80%9Cdumped%E2%80%9D%20by%20the%20prosecution%20in%20the%20form%20of%20so-called%20electronic%20evidence%2C%20the%20trial%20court%20pulled%20out%20a%20variety%20of%20unique%20incriminating%20material.%20One%20of%20which%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Cbanana%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20just%20a%20banana%2C%20a%20newspaper%20and%20an%20umbrella%20too.%20The%20court%20had%20found%20from%20the%20cache%20of%20literature%20one%20particular%20newspaper%20article%20which%20mentioned%20that%20Naxals%20supposedly%20carried%20a%20%E2%80%9Cbanana%2C%20umbrella%20and%20newspaper%E2%80%9D%20as%20code%20to%20identify%20each%20other%20(i.e.%2C%20to%20identify%20highly%20secretive%20Maoists).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trial%20judge%20held%2C%20%E2%80%9C%5BI%5Dn%20order%20to%20identify%20the%20members%20of%20CPI%20Maoist%20or%20RDF%20organisation%20by%20an%20unknown%20person%20the%20unique%20identification%2C%20i.e.%2C%20Banana%2C%20Umbrella%20and%20Newspaper%20were%20used.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDid%20the%20investigating%20officer%20call%20it%20the%20modus%20operandi%20of%20%E2%80%98Urban%20Naxals%E2%80%99%3F%20The%20answer%20is%20no.%20Did%20any%20witness%20of%20the%20prosecution%20say%20that%20this%20was%20the%20modus%20operandi%3F%20The%20answer%20is%20another%20no.%20No%20one%20said%20it%2C%20no%20one%20hinted%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhere%20did%20it%20come%20from%20then%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20journalist%20had%20written%20it%20in%20one%20of%20her%20articles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWas%20she%20examined%20as%20a%20witness%20by%20the%20prosecution%3F%20No.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20item%20became%20a%20fatal%20piece%20of%20%E2%80%98evidence%E2%80%99%20for%20the%20defence%2C%20in%20that%20the%20journalist%20in%20question%20had%20written%20in%20her%20article%20that%20she%20carried%20these%20three%20items%20to%20meet%20Naxals.%20Hence%20proved%20that%20these%20items%20are%20incriminatory%20articles.%20Possession%20of%20which%2C%20inter%20alia%2C%20proved%20a%20person%20to%20be%20a%20Naxal%20for%20whom%20life%20imprisonment%20was%20not%20punishment%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20question%20would%20be%3A%20Were%20any%20of%20the%20accused%20in%20the%20case%20caught%20possessing%20any%20of%20these%20three%20items%3F%20The%20answer%20is%20no%2C%20not%20really.%20But%20Pandu%20Narote%20was%20found%20carrying%20an%20umbrella%20when%20he%20was%20arrested%20in%20August%2C%20a%20season%20of%20rains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrashant%20Rahi%2C%20arrested%20about%20a%20week%20later%2C%20was%20found%20carrying%20not%20just%20a%20full%2C%20completely%20intact%20newspaper%20but%20cuttings%20of%20another%20newspaper%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(Maybe%20he%20just%20wanted%20to%20ensure%20that%20in%20case%20he%20lost%20the%20newspaper%2C%20he%20could%20flash%20around%20cuttings%20to%20attract%20his%20fellow%20secretive%20Naxals%20hiding%20in%20the%20dense%20forest.)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWas%20anyone%20apprehended%20carrying%20a%20banana%3F%20No.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20the%20prosecution%20could%20have%20made%20an%20argument%20that%20the%20incriminating%20evidence%2C%20i.e.%2C%20bananas%2C%20were%20eaten%20by%20these%20persons%20and%2C%20therefore%2C%20they%20have%20committed%20another%20offence%2C%20that%20of%20destroying%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20was%20also%20not%20to%20be.%20The%20prosecution%20did%20not%20utter%20a%20word%20about%20this%20so-called%20modus%20operandi%20and%20the%20utterly%20banal%20but%20most%20incriminating%20items.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20learned%20judge%2C%20however%2C%20held%20that%20since%20Prashant%20Rahi%20was%20found%20possessing%20a%20newspaper%2C%20%E2%80%9Chence%2C%20in%20peculiar%20facts%20and%20circumstances%20of%20the%20case%20finding%20of%20the%20daily%20newspaper%20Dainik%20Bhaskar%20can%20be%20considered%20as%20incriminating%20evidence%20against%20accused%20no.%204%20Prashant%20Rahi.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch4%3E%3Cb%3EFigments%20of%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cb%3E%3Ci%3Epanchnamas%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh4%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20search%2C%20seizure%20and%20arrest%20of%20Prashant%20Rahi%20is%20another%20episode%20in%20which%20the%20court%20did%20not%20find%20any%20fault.%20The%20prosecution%20alleged%20that%20they%20got%20secret%20information%20that%20the%20second%20messenger%20(Prashant%20Rahi%2C%20the%20first%20one%20being%20Hem%20Mishra)%20was%20going%20to%20be%20at%20Devri%2C%20a%20remote%20town%20in%20Gadchiroli%2C%20on%20September%201%2C%202013%2C%20to%20meet%20senior%20Naxals%20to%20pass%20on%20some%20secret%20message.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccordingly%2C%20a%20team%20that%20was%20already%20in%20the%20area%20searching%20for%20one%20Pahadsing%20was%20given%20this%20information.%20Who%20gave%20the%20information%20to%20the%20search%20party%3F%20Neither%20the%20recipient%20stated%20it%2C%20nor%20the%20giver%20stated%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnyways%2C%20the%20information%20was%20that%20an%20accused%20in%20the%20case%20was%20in%20the%20Raipur%20area%20and%20the%20search%20party%20should%20look%20for%20him.%20Did%20the%20information%20contain%20a%20physical%20description%20of%20the%20person%20to%20be%20looked%20for%3F%20Not%20stated.%20Did%20they%20know%20the%20name%20of%20the%20accused%3F%20Not%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccordingly%2C%20the%20prosecution%20claim%20went%20on%2C%20the%20search%20party%20went%20to%20Raipur%20wherein%20they%20found%20out%20that%20the%20accused%20had%20gone%20towards%20Devri%20in%20a%20four-wheeler.%20So%2C%20they%20went%20to%20Devri.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20Devri%2C%20two%20persons%20(Prashant%20Rahi%20and%20Vijay%20Nan%20Tirki)%20were%20intercepted%20at%20%E2%80%9Ca%20crowded%20junction%E2%80%9D.%20They%20were%20taken%20in%20custody%20(at%204%3A30%20p.m.%20on%20the%20same%20day%2C%20i.e.%2C%20September%201%2C%202013)%20as%20they%20were%20in%20a%20%E2%80%9Csuspicious%20condition%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20were%20found%20to%20be%20possessing%20%E2%80%9CMaowadi%E2%80%9D%20(Maoist)%20and%20%E2%80%9CNaxal%20literature%E2%80%9D.%20Upon%20merely%20being%20asked%2C%20they%20revealed%20their%20true%20identity.%20Then%2C%20as%20per%20directions%20of%20the%20sub-divisional%20police%20officer%20(SDPO)%20Suhas%20Bawache%2C%20they%20were%20brought%20to%20Aheri%20at%205%20a.m.%20the%20next%20day%2C%20i.e.%2C%20September%202%2C%202013.%20No%20arrest%20or%20seizure%20panchnama%20was%20drawn%20on%20the%20spot%20or%20at%20Devri.%20It%20came%20to%20be%20drawn%20at%20Aheri%20the%20next%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20panch%20witness%20to%20this%20seizure%20stated%20that%20he%20had%20gone%20to%20the%20police%20station%20for%20this%20panchnama%20on%20September%202%2C%202013%20in%20the%20evening%20at%205%3A45%20p.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20during%20this%20search%20again%20that%20Prashant%20Rahi%20was%20found%20possessing%20Maoist%20literature.%20Meaning%20that%20after%20about%2024%20hours%20since%20his%20custody%2C%20he%20continued%20to%20possess%20the%20said%20Maoist%20literature.%20(Perhaps%20the%20police%20party%20found%20incriminating%20material%20with%20them%20at%20Devri%20Chichgad%20T%20point%2C%20read%20it%20and%20returned%20it%20earnestly%20to%20the%20accused%20for%20it%20belonged%20to%20them%2C%20and%20seized%20it%20the%20next%20day%20at%20their%20leisure.%20What%20was%20the%20tearing%20hurry%3F)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20what%20was%20found%20in%20the%20possession%20of%20the%20accused%20after%2024%20hours%20of%20custody%20is%20equally%20interesting.%20A%20wallet%20containing%20some%20cash%2C%20a%20PAN%20card%2C%20a%20driving%20license%2C%2012%20visiting%20cards%2C%20of%20course%2C%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20newspaper%20Dainik%20Bhaskar%2C%20one%20transparent%20plastic%20folder%20containing%20four%20empty%20envelopes%2C%20photocopies%20of%20Dainik%20Bhaskar%20(newspaper%20cutting)%2C%20a%20few%20blank%20papers%2C%20a%20few%20prison%20and%20court-related%20documents%20and%20%E2%80%9Cthree%20English%20stapled%20Naxal%20organisation-related%20documents%E2%80%9D.%20(These%20three%20English-stapled%20Naxal%20organisation-related%20documents%20could%20not%20be%20traced%20in%20the%20hearing%20before%20the%20high%20court%2C%20though%20counsels%20on%20both%20sides%20searched%20for%20them%20repeatedly%20and%20fervently).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20court%20were%20%E2%80%9Cclosed%E2%80%9D%20by%20provisions%20of%20law%2C%20saving%20the%20accused%20from%20the%20gallows%2C%20it%20did%20not%20stop%20the%20court%20from%20dispensing%20with%20the%20requirement%20of%20proof%20beyond%20reasonable%20doubt%20and%20extending%20the%20benefit%20of%20probability%20to%20the%20prosecution.%20It%20held%2C%20%E2%80%9CVersion%20of%20prosecution%20appears%20to%20be%20more%20probable%20than%20the%20defence.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20short%2C%20a%20terrorist%20on%20a%20mission%20carrying%20extremely%20sensitive%20secret%20information%20that%20was%20to%20be%20given%20to%20the%20senior%20terrorists%20hiding%20in%20the%20forest%20was%20so%20na%C3%AFve%20that%20he%20carried%20with%20him%20all%20his%20identity%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20did%20not%20just%20carry%20one%20identity%20card%2C%20but%20multiple%20ID%20cards%2C%20along%20with%20his%20train%20tickets%20and%20visiting%20cards.%20He%20did%20not%20make%20an%20effort%20to%20conceal%20his%20identity%20and%20on%20merely%20being%20asked%20was%20polite%20enough%20to%20reveal%20his%20true%20name%20along%20with%20his%20other%20aliases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20secret%20information%20can%20only%20be%20related%20to%20court%20and%20prison%20documents%2C%20or%20newspaper%20cuttings%20of%20which%20photocopies%20were%20found%20kept%20in%20a%20transparent%20blue%20plastic%20folder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20one%20knows%20what%20was%20in%20those%20stapled%20pages.%20The%20trial%20court%20has%20not%20commented%20on%20it%20in%20its%20judgment.%20All%20said%2C%20the%20fact%20remains%20that%20%3Cem%3EDainik%20Bhaskar%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20inter%20alia%2C%20sealed%20the%20fate%20of%20Prashant%20Rahi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20Pandu%20Narote%20and%20Mahesh%20Tirki%2C%20who%20were%20allegedly%20on%20a%20secret%20mission%20to%20transport%20Hem%20Mishra%20secretly%20to%20senior%20Naxals%20in%20the%20remote%20forest%2C%20were%20found%20carrying%20all%20identity%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPandu%20was%20found%20possessing%20not%20just%20one%20identity%20document%2C%20he%20was%20carrying%20his%20domicile%20certificate%2C%20caste%20certificate%2C%20bank%20passbook%2C%20his%20own%20birth%20certificate%2C%20the%20birth%20certificate%20of%20his%20daughter%2C%20ration%20card%2C%20driving%20licence%2C%20election%20identity%20card%2C%20school%20leaving%20certificate%20and%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20Lokmat%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMahesh%20carried%20propaganda%20material%20of%20Naxals%2C%20i.e.%2C%20three%20pamphlets%2C%20all%20different%2C%20and%20of%20course%20an%20election%20ID%20card.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHem%20Mishra%20was%20carrying%20an%20ATM%20Card%2C%20PAN%20card%2C%20election%20ID%20card%2C%20university%20library%20identity%20card%2C%20yatri%20card%2C%20railway%20ticket%20from%20Delhi%20to%20Ballarshah%2C%20one%20Kodak%20digital%20camera%20with%20a%20charger%2C%20a%2016GB%20memory%20card%2C%20and%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20Sahara%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENone%20of%20these%20three%20tried%20to%20conceal%20their%20identity.%20They%20gave%20away%20their%20true%20names%20right%20away.%20They%20did%20not%20even%20try%20to%20run%20away%20upon%20being%20intercepted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2016GB%20memory%20card%20which%20contained%20%E2%80%9Cvital%20Maoist%20communication%20and%20other%20Maoist%20documents%20in%20encrypted%20form%20with%20the%20intention%20to%20further%20activities%20of%20terrorist%20organisation%20CPI%20Maoist%E2%80%9D%20to%20be%20handed%20over%20to%20a%20senior%20terrorist%20in%20the%20forest%2C%20contained%20some%20of%20Hem%20Mishra%E2%80%99s%20own%20personal%20photographs%2C%20photographs%20of%20Professor%20Saibaba%20and%20his%20family%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20contained%20a%20few%20movies%E2%80%94%20really%20boring%20ones.%20Not%20even%20worth%20a%20name.%20Among%20all%20these%20contents%2C%20it%20was%20stated%20that%20there%20were%20incriminating%20documents.%20They%20were%20incriminating%20solely%20because%20they%20were%20protected%20by%20a%20password.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20not%20a%20whisper%20as%20to%20what%20efforts%20were%20taken%20to%20decrypt%20the%20password.%20But%20since%20they%20were%20password%20protected%2C%20they%20were%20termed%20incriminatory.%20Could%20they%20be%20bank%20e-statements%3F%20Or%20income%20tax%20e-returns%3F%20No%20one%20knows.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch4%3E%3Cb%3EA%20search%20to%20seize%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh4%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20seizure%20at%20the%20house%20of%20Professor%20Saibaba%20is%20another%20episode.%20Around%2050%20high-ranking%20officials%20from%20Gadchiroli%20and%20Delhi%20were%20party%20to%20this%20sensational%20raid.%20Professor%20Saibaba%E2%80%99s%20house%20was%20located%20in%20Delhi%20University%20Campus%2C%20surrounded%20by%20houses%20of%20many%20professors%20and%20university%20employees.%20Yet%20the%20witness%20chosen%20was%20an%20illiterate%20poor%20barber.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdmittedly%2C%20Professor%20Saibaba%20and%20the%20%3Ci%3Epanch%20%3C%2Fi%3Ewere%20locked%20outside%20the%20house%20while%20the%20search%20was%20going%20on.%20The%20%3Ci%3Epanch%20%3C%2Fi%3Ehimself%20requested%20that%20some%20other%20educated%20person%20be%20made%20a%20%3Ci%3Epanch%20%3C%2Fi%3Ewitness%20for%20he%20is%20illiterate%20but%20that%20was%20not%20accepted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Professor%20Saibaba%20appealed%20in%20writing%20to%20take%20a%20search%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20professors%20or%20lawyers%20who%20were%20present%2C%20but%20that%20too%20was%20denied.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20witness%20admitted%20being%20kept%20outside%20the%20house%20while%20the%20search%20was%20ongoing%2C%20the%20court%20found%20exceptional%20reason%20to%20give%20no%20importance%20to%20that%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%2C%20in%20Paragraph%20230%20holds%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20to%20be%20noted%20that%20this%20witness%20is%20illiterate.%20He%20cannot%20read%20and%20write%20the%20English%20language%20and%20his%20cross-examination%20was%20held%20the%20whole%20day%2C%20that%20too%20by%20an%20eminent%20lawyer%20having%20standing%20practice%20of%20more%20than%2025%20years%20and%20this%20witness%20might%20have%20been%20frightened%20because%20of%20the%20atmosphere%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHence%2C%20a%20stray%20admission%20%E2%80%A6%20that%20he%20and%20the%20accused%20Saibaba%20(were)%20kept%20outside%20the%20house%20while%20taking%20house%20search%20%E2%80%A6%20is%20not%20a%20ground%20to%20discard%20version%20of%20the%20prosecution%20witness.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBack%20to%20the%20day%20of%20the%20raid%20at%20Professor%20Saibaba%E2%80%99s%20house.%20Admittedly%2C%20about%2050%20police%20officers%20were%20inside%20the%20house%2C%20and%20along%20with%20them%20were%20two%20cyber%20experts.%20Complete%20videography%20was%20done%20of%20the%20seizures.%20After%20hours%20of%20search%20and%20seizure%2C%20they%20gathered%20all%20the%20electronic%20material.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20seized%20material%20was%20taken%20in%20a%20bag%20and%20the%20police%20left%20it.%20Just%20like%20one%20goes%20to%20a%20vegetable%20market%2C%20stuffs%20various%20purchases%20in%20the%20bag%20and%20goes%20home%20thinking%20about%20which%20dish%20to%20cook%20from%20so%20many%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20hash%20value%20was%20drawn%20or%20given%20as%20the%20law%20requires%2C%20nor%20were%20the%20devices%20sealed%20to%20avoid%20interference%20or%20manipulation.%20I%20repeat%2C%20there%20was%20no%20sealing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes!%20The%20most%20basic%20thing%20that%20is%20done%20in%20search%20and%20seizure%E2%80%94%20sealing.%20Putting%20seized%20articles%20in%20a%20cover%2C%20and%20then%20sealing%20it%20with%20the%20signature%20of%20the%20%3Ci%3Epanch%20%3C%2Fi%3Ewitnesses%2C%20police%20officers%2C%20etc.%20That%20was%20not%20done.%20They%20only%20drew%20an%20inventory%2C%20and%2C%20like%20I%20said%2C%20placed%20the%20items%20in%20a%20bag%20and%20left.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20happened%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20two%20%E2%80%98cyber%20experts%E2%80%99.%20These%20two%20%E2%80%98cyber%20experts%E2%80%99%20could%20not%20differentiate%20between%20a%20Bluetooth%20device%20and%20a%20pen%20drive%2C%20hence%20they%20recorded%20that%20the%20attachment%20to%20the%20laptop%20was%20a%20pen%20drive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20mistake%20was%20repeated%20even%20at%20the%20Aheri%20police%20station%2C%20where%20another%20%E2%80%98cyber%20expert%E2%80%99%20called%20the%20attachment%20to%20the%20laptop%20a%20pen%20drive.%20It%20was%2C%20however%2C%20in%20the%20analysis%20report%20that%20the%20device%20attached%20to%20the%20laptop%20was%20found%20to%20be%20a%20Bluetooth%20device.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESurendra%20Gadling%2C%20cross-examining%20the%20investigating%20officer%2C%20asked%20him%20why%20the%20videography%20of%20the%20raid%20had%20not%20been%20filed%20on%20record.%20Is%20it%20because%20in%20the%20videography%20police%20officers%20were%20seen%20planting%20hard%20discs%20and%20other%20materials%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20witness%20said%2C%20a%20CD%20of%20the%20videography%20was%20not%20provided%20by%20the%20Delhi%20police%2C%20even%20though%20he%20had%20reminded%20them%20four%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20was%20the%20reminder%20given%2C%20written%20or%20oral%3F%20Answer%3A%20Oral.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20high%20court%2C%20when%20the%20Bench%20asked%20the%20special%20counsel%20to%20procure%20that%20video%20recording%20and%20show%20it%20to%20the%20court%2C%20the%20prosecution%20said%20it%20would%20get%20it.%20However%2C%20the%20video%20recording%20never%20came.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENone%20of%20these%20created%20any%20doubt%20in%20the%20mind%20of%20the%20trial%20court.%20They%20were%20all%20%3Ci%3E%E2%80%9Cstray%3C%2Fi%3E%E2%80%9D%20incidents%20that%20could%20not%20divert%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20single-minded%20focus%20from%20finding%20the%20accused%20guilty.%20Not%20fatal%20to%20the%20prosecution%2C%20owing%20to%20cross-examination%20by%20an%20eminent%20lawyer%2C%20who%20is%20now%20in%20jail%20on%20more%20ridiculous%2C%20trumped-up%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch4%3E%3Cb%3ENon-cognisance%20of%20ill-treatment%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh4%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20apart%2C%20the%20evidence%20of%20the%20judicial%20magistrate%20first%20class%20who%20recorded%20the%20alleged%20confession%20of%20Pandu%20(now%20deceased)%20and%20Vijay%20makes%20for%20an%20even%20more%20disheartening%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPandu%20and%20Vijay%20had%20both%20addressed%20a%20detailed%20letter%20to%20the%20magistrate%20complaining%20about%20the%20ill-treatment%20that%20was%20meted%20out%20to%20them%20which%20was%20not%20acted%20upon.%20During%20the%20cross-examination%20when%20the%20judicial%20officer%20was%20countered%20with%20it%2C%20he%20gave%20the%20following%20reply.%20Try%20making%20sense%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Ci%3ENone%20of%20the%20accused%20had%20made%20an%20application%20before%20me%20about%20the%20ill-treatment%20by%20police%20during%20the%20investigation.%20It%20is%20true%20that%20the%20accused%20in%20the%20present%20case%20made%20a%20written%20application%20before%20me%20about%20ill-treatment%20meted%20out%20to%20them%20after%20recording%20their%20statement.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Ci%3EI%20had%20not%20taken%20any%20action%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20their%20written%20application.%20I%20did%20not%20call%20any%20report%20from%20the%20police%20officer.%20I%20did%20not%20take%20cognisance%20of%20their%20complaints.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Ci%3EI%20did%20not%20take%20cognisance%20because%20before%20recording%20the%20confession%20when%20it%20was%20being%20recorded%2C%20I%20came%20to%20know%20that%20said%20the%20confession%20was%20voluntarily%20made%20and%20an%20application%20for%20ill-treatment%20was%20made%20subsequently%20hence%2C%20I%20did%20not%20take%20any%20cognisance.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Ci%3ENow%2C%20I%20am%20shown%20the%20complaint%20made%20by%20the%20accused%20in%20the%20present%20proceedings%20regarding%20ill-treatment.%20The%20complaint%20bears%20my%20signature%20about%20receipt%20of%20the%20same.%20It%20is%20marked%20at%20Exh%20292.%20(document%20exhibited%20as%20it%20is%20referred%20by%20defence.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Ci%3EOn%20the%20said%20application%20on%20October%208%2C%20I%20called%20say%20of%20APP%20(sic).%20As%20the%20said%20application%20was%20received%20through%20an%20envelope%2C%20I%20directed%20my%20staff%20of%20the%20court%20to%20file%20it%20with%20case%20papers%20and%20there%20was%20an%20endorsement%20to%20that%20effect%20on%20it.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Ci%3EBut%20the%20clerk%20of%20the%20court%20did%20not%20put%20it%20before%20me.%20On%20October%208%2C%20I%20called%20say%20of%20APP%20at%20that%20time%20the%20said%20application%20was%20not%20attached%20to%20the%20case%20papers.%20When%20the%20application%20was%20put%20before%20me%20on%20the%20third%20and%20eighth%2C%20I%20had%20gone%20through%20the%20entire%20contents%20of%20the%20application.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Ci%3EI%20had%20not%20taken%20any%20action%20on%20the%20said%20application.%20As%20the%20application%20was%20not%20again%20put%20up%20before%20me%20after%20obtaining%20say%20of%20APP%2C%20I%20did%20not%20pass%20any%20order.%20The%20said%20application%20was%20not%20put%20up%20before%20me%20after%20obtaining%20say%20of%20APP%20after%20my%20Order%20on%20October%208.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Ci%3EI%20did%20not%20call%20the%20say%20of%20police.%20As%20it%20was%20a%20complaint%20against%20the%20police%2C%20I%20did%20not%20call%20the%20say%20of%20APP.%20Not%20true%20to%20say%20that%20as%20the%20said%20confession%20was%20recorded%20under%20the%20inducement%20and%20threat%20of%20police%2C%20I%20did%20not%20call%20the%20say%20of%20police.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Ci%3EWhen%20there%20is%20a%20complaint%20disclosing%20commission%20of%20cognisable%20offence%2C%20then%20the%20magistrate%20has%20to%20take%20cognisance%20of%20the%20offence.%20It%20is%20not%20true%20to%20say%20that%20in%20order%20to%20assist%20the%20investigation%2C%20I%20did%20not%20take%20cognisance%20of%20the%20offence%20in%20respect%20of%20allegations%20made%20at%20Exh.%20292.%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cb%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Ci%3EDuring%20my%20tenure%20at%20Aheri%20I%20used%20to%20reside%20in%20the%20quarter%20constructed%20by%20police%20officers.%20Witness%20volunteers%20that%20as%20there%20was%20no%20judicial%20assigned%20quarter%20and%20he%20had%20made%20an%20application%20to%20the%20then%20PDJ%20for%20assigning%20quarter%20and%20as%20the%20whole%20Gadchiroli%20district%20is%20a%20Naxalite%20area%20for%20security%20purposes%2C%20the%20quarter%20was%20assigned%20to%20me.%20Hence%20I%20was%20residing%20there%3C%2Fi%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch4%3E%3Cb%3EWho%20will%20judge%20the%20(mis)judge%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh4%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20see%20the%20chronology%20of%20events.%20Hem%20Mishra%20is%20declared%20arrested%20on%20August%2022%2C%202013.%20National%20media%20carries%20the%20news.%20Prashant%20Rahi%E2%80%99s%20is%20declared%20arrested%20on%20September%202%2C%202013.%20The%20national%20media%20carries%20the%20news.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20these%20two%20arrests%2C%20there%20was%20a%20report%20in%20a%20national%20newspaper%20hinting%20that%20Professor%20Saibaba%20was%20on%20the%20radar%20of%20security%20agencies.%20In%20view%20of%20this%20report%2C%20colleagues%20of%20the%20professor%20addressed%20a%20letter%20to%20P.%20Chidambaram%2C%20the%20then%20Union%20Home%20Minister%2C%20suspecting%20mischief%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20security%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20these%20circumstances%2C%20is%20it%20believable%20that%20an%20intellectual%20person%20of%20the%20calibre%20of%20Professor%20Saibaba%20would%20keep%20all%20incriminating%20materials%20in%20his%20own%20house%2C%20in%20his%20laptop%2C%20in%20his%20hard%20disc%2C%20so%20that%20it%20becomes%20easier%20for%20police%20to%20nab%20him%20and%20fix%20him%20for%20good%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20person%20having%20the%20slightest%20of%20guilt%20on%20the%20smallest%20of%20hints%20will%20put%20himself%20on%20guard.%20He%20will%20watch%20his%20back.%20Erase%20all%20traces.%20Clean%20himself%20to%20the%20extent%20possible.%20Make%20desperate%20attempts%20to%20destroy%20any%20and%20every%20evidence.%20That%20would%20be%20natural%20conduct.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20was%20nothing%20natural%20in%20this%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20being%20the%20case%2C%20where%20arrest%2C%20search%20and%20seizure%20were%20the%20most%20important%20factors%2C%20bereft%20of%20any%20evidence%20the%20court%20saying%20that%20life%20imprisonment%20was%20not%20sufficient%20gives%20reason%20to%20say%20that%20the%20judicial%20officer%20was%20biased%2C%20if%20not%20motivated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECould%20it%20have%20been%20an%20error%20or%20%E2%80%98errors%E2%80%99%2C%20when%20records%20are%20overwhelmingly%20full%20with%20all%20reasons%20to%20not%20believe%20the%20prosecution%E2%80%99s%20case%3F%20Could%20it%20have%20been%20ignorance%20of%20the%20law%2C%20when%20reading%20in%20evidence%20what%20is%20not%20brought%20on%20records%3F%20Could%20it%20have%20been%20a%20lack%20of%20judicial%20approach%3F%20What%20could%20it%20be%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESadly%20however%2C%20the%20argument%20of%20Pradeep%20Mandhyan%20that%20the%20findings%20and%20judgment%20of%20the%20trial%20court%20are%20%E2%80%9Cperverse%2C%20dishonest%20and%20corrupt%E2%80%9D%20remain%20undecided%2C%20and%20will%20remain%20undecided%2C%20forever.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENihalsing%20B.%20Rathod%20is%20a%20lawyer%20based%20in%20Nagpur.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20first%20appeared%20on%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheleaflet.in%5C%22%3EThe%20Leaflet%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20and%20has%20been%20published%20here%20with%20permission.%20Read%20the%20original%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheleaflet.in%2Fwas-the-tri