nario.%20To%20the%20west%2C%20the%20Maldives%20glories%20in%20an%20%E2%80%9CIndia%20out%E2%80%9D%20policy%2C%20Pakistan%20remains%20Pakistan%2C%20unchanged%20either%20by%20Modi%20dropping%20in%20unexpectedly%20to%20attend%20Nawaz%20Sharif%E2%80%99s%20granddaughter%E2%80%99s%20wedding%2C%20or%20dropping%20bombs%20on%20some%20random%20hillside%2C%20and%20our%20great%20hope%20in%20Afghanistan%20is%20to%20snuggle%20up%20to%20the%20Taliban.%20To%20the%20north%2C%20India%20dug%20a%20hole%20for%20itself%20with%20a%20blockade%20of%20Nepal%20in%20order%20to%20bully%20it%20to%20change%20its%20Constitution.%20It%20is%20still%20trying%20to%20dig%20itself%20out%20of%20that%20hole.%20Even%20further%20north%2C%20the%20loss%20of%20deterrence%20against%20China%20has%20been%20so%20severe%20that%20Modi%20has%20not%20publicly%20uttered%20the%20name%20of%20China%20in%20nearly%20four%20years.%20Apparently%20swinging%20in%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ejhoola%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ewith%20Xi%20Jinping%2C%20and%20then%20force-feeding%20him%20and%20his%20wife%20Gujarati%20vegetarian%20food%20for%20three%20days%20running%20was%20not%20a%20diplomatically%20sound%20manoeuvre.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20our%20east%2C%20an%20increasingly%20authoritarian%20and%20corrupt%20Bangladeshi%20government%20loves%20us%20for%20certifying%20their%20elections%20as%20%E2%80%9Cfree%20and%20fair%E2%80%9D%2C%20but%20then%20the%20Selection%20Commission%20of%20India%20is%20happy%20to%20do%20just%20that.%20Nonetheless%2C%20it%20is%20China%20that%20has%20supplied%20two%20thirds%20of%20Bangladeshi%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffeatures.csis.org%2Fsnapshots%2Fchina-submarine-diplomacy%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Emilitary%20imports%20since%202010%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%20is%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newagebd.net%2Farticle%2F227017%2Fbangladesh-seeks-more-chinese-investment-in-power-energy-sector%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epreferred%20investor%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20its%20energy%20sector.%20Of%20course%2C%20with%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20engendering%20a%20civil%20war%20in%20Manipur%2C%20and%20the%20always%20unintelligent%20Amit%20Shah%20wanting%20to%20fence%20the%20border%20with%20Myanmar%2C%20the%20Look%20East%20Policy%20which%20was%20supposed%20to%20become%20the%20Act%20East%20Policy%2C%20is%20burning%20with%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20corpses%20created%20by%20communalism.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20the%20south%2C%20we%20have%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20of%20which%20the%20less%20said%20is%20the%20better.%20Although%2C%20maybe%20to%20the%20south%20is%20South%20India%2C%20because%20the%20level%20of%20fraud%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20has%20committed%20in%20squeezing%20tax%20from%20the%20southern%20states%20is%20promoting%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fkarnataka%2Finjustice-to-southern-states-may-compel-demand-for-separate-nation-congress-mp-d-k-suresh-2875383%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etalk%20of%20secession%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20And%20all%20this%20without%20counting%20the%20fact%20that%20under%20Modi%20economic%20growth%20has%20faltered%20and%20choked%2C%20India%20has%20seen%20the%20highest%20rates%20of%20unemployment%20since%20it%20started%20measuring%20unemployment%2C%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Findia%2Findias-30093-new-covid-19-cases-are-lowest-daily-figure-4-mths-2021-07-20%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E4.9%20million%20Indians%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20died%20because%20Modi%20bungled%20the%20Covid-19%20crisis.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUnderstanding%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20popularity%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20yet%2C%20by%20all%20accounts%20and%20surveys%2C%20Modi%20is%20spectacularly%20popular.%20People%2C%20it%20seems%2C%20are%20willing%20to%20ignore%20the%20obvious%20untruth%20of%20his%20college%20degree%20in%20Entire%20Political%20Science%2C%20after%20all%20he%20has%20said%20so%20himself%20in%20at%20least%20one%20speech%20and%20one%20televised%20interview%20with%20Rajeev%20Shukla.%20They%20approve%20of%20his%20story%20about%20running%20a%20tea%20stall%20on%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F890416%2Fliquid-nala-gas-twitter-cracks-up-on-narendra-modis-comment-about-making-tea-from-gutter-fumes%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Egutter%20gas%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20extracting%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgulfnews.com%2Fworld%2Fasia%2Findia%2Findia-pm-modi-trolled-after-saying-extract-oxygen-from-air-using-a-wind-turbine-1.1602250227541%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eoxygen%20from%20the%20air%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20using%20wind%20turbines%20to%20%E2%80%9Ccapture%20the%20oxygen%20market%E2%80%9D.%20Even%20his%20obsessive%20love%20for%20English%20acronyms%20is%20pardoned.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPart%20of%20this%20popularity%20may%20be%20fraudulent%2C%20manufactured%20through%20so%20much%20money%20spent%20on%20advertisements%2C%20that%20the%20face%20of%20Modi%2C%20can%20be%20found%20from%20everything%20from%20grain%20bags%20to%20petrol%20station.%20On%20television%2C%20propagandists%20cosplaying%20as%20journalists%20crow%20about%20masterstroke%20after%20masterstroke%2C%20no%20doubt%20in%20hopes%20of%20being%20stroked%20by%20their%20master.%20But%20it%20is%20worth%20asking%20if%20it%20is%20exactly%20this%2C%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20manifest%20unfitness%20for%20the%20office%20he%20occupies%2C%20which%20is%20part%20of%20his%20appeal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fmodi-government-pannu-assassination%5C%22%3EWhatever%20%E2%80%98Rogue%E2%80%99%20Yarn%20the%20Modi%20Government%20May%20Spin%20on%20Pannun%20Plot%2C%20There%E2%80%99ll%20Be%20No%20Happy%20Ending%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20a%20broken%20primary%20education%20system%2C%20and%20an%20economy%20where%20dignified%20jobs%20are%20achieved%20only%20through%20superhuman%20effort%20or%20some%20form%20of%20corruption%20%E2%80%93%20either%20monetary%20or%20through%20caste%20and%20clan%20networks%20%E2%80%93%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20Indians%20have%20few%20reasons%20to%20believe%20they%20will%20achieve%20anything%20through%20honesty%20and%20hard%20work.%20Even%20were%20they%20able%20to%20occupy%20a%20position%20of%20authority%20they%20are%2C%20like%20Modi%2C%20likely%20to%20find%20it%20beyond%20their%20capability.%20Success%2C%20therefore%2C%20is%20then%20no%20longer%20a%20matter%20of%20skill%2C%20effort%2C%20or%20honest%20competition.%20Modi%20demonstrates%20for%20them%20that%20someone%20like%20him%20and%20thereby%20them%2C%20can%20continue%20to%20enjoy%20the%20pelf%20and%20power%20of%20office.%20They%20may%20be%20thinking%20that%20all%20one%20needs%20to%20do%20is%20rig%20the%20system%2C%20buy%20or%20bully%20any%20opposition%2C%20and%20simply%20refuse%20to%20answer%20any%20questions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUnfair%20to%20blame%20Modi%20alone%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20an%20essay%20on%20leadership%2C%20the%20former%2C%20criminal%2C%20president%20of%20the%20United%20States%2C%20Richard%20Nixon%2C%20wrote%20that%20a%20leader%20is%20somebody%20who%20has%20followers.%20This%20simple%20formulation%20hides%20a%20multiplicity%20of%20interpretations.%20You%20can%20be%20a%20leader%20of%20those%20who%20desire%20to%20be%20better%2C%20do%20better%2C%20and%20who%20look%20to%20you%20to%20inspire%20and%20support%20you%20in%20that.%20Or%20you%20can%20be%20a%20leader%20of%20those%20who%20are%20haunted%20by%20a%20fear%20that%20they%20are%20worthless%2C%20and%20look%20to%20you%20to%20show%20how%20even%20without%20any%20grace%2C%20capability%2C%20or%20achievement%2C%20they%20can%20get%20things%20through%2