%80%99%20grade%20mushrooms%2C%20which%2C%20due%20to%20irregular%20shapes%2C%20are%20sold%20to%20food%20processing%20companies%20for%20canning%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOperating%20under%20the%20brand%20names%20Gupta%20Organic%20Farms%20and%20A3R%20Mushroom%20Farms%2C%20the%20brothers%20market%20their%20products%20to%20businesses%20and%20direct%20consumers.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20supply%20to%20numerous%20businesses%20in%20Agra%20and%20Delhi%2C%20and%20there%E2%80%99s%20significant%20consumer%20demand%20in%20the%20city.%20In%20total%2C%20our%20monthly%20sales%20exceed%20Rs%201%20lakh.%20Our%20annual%20turnover%20stands%20at%20Rs%207.5%20crores%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAyush%20underscores%20the%20brand%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20to%20providing%20the%20best%20to%20its%20customers%2C%20emphasising%20that%20no%20chemicals%20are%20used%20to%20aid%20growth.%20%E2%80%9CAll%20our%20vegetables%20and%20mushrooms%20are%20grown%20organically%2C%20without%20the%20use%20of%20any%20chemical%20fertilisers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20840px)%20100vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fmushroom-3-1-1710404400.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20brother%20earns%20a%20turnover%20of%20Rs%207.5%20crore%20every%20year.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fmushroom-3-1-1710404400.jpg%20840w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fmushroom-3-1-1710404400-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fmushroom-3-1-1710404400-500x261.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fmushroom-3-1-1710404400-768x401.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fmushroom-3-1-1710404400-1