ng%20and%20preserving%20the%20traditional%20crafts.%20On%20display%20are%20traditional%20art%20forms%20including%20%E2%80%98Chitrakathi%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20the%20art%20of%20telling%20stories%20through%20pictures%2C%20%E2%80%98Kal%20Sutli%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20a%20traditional%20form%20of%20string%20puppetry%20and%20shadow%20puppetry.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fpuppetry_11zon-1710845512.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shadow%20and%20string%20puppetry%20have%20been%20the%20pride%20of%20the%20Thakkar%20Adivasi%20community%20in%20India%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fpuppetry_11zon-1710845512.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fpuppetry_11zon-1710845512-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fpuppetry_11zon-1710845512-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fpuppetry_11zon-1710845512-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fpuppetry_11zon-1710845512-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345197%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EShadow%20and%20string%20puppetry%20have%20been%20the%20pride%20of%20the%20Thakkar%20Adivasi%20community%20in%20India%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Rashmi%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20the%20arts%20complex%2C%20Sawant%20was%20intent%20on%20helping%20the%20women%20earn%20through%20a%20craft%20they%20knew%20best%20%E2%80%94%20food.%20Under%20the%20banner%20%E2%80%98Hirkani%E2%80%99%2C%20Sawant%20also%20mobilised%20160%20SHGs%20through%20which%20300%20women%20were%20en