%20and%20then%20observe%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBefore%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20I%20ask%20them%20to%20send%20their%20inputs%20and%20give%20them%20feedback.%20We%20also%20advise%20them%20on%20the%20kind%20of%20body%20language%20and%20type%20of%20answers%20required%20during%20these%20interviews.%20And%20then%20I%20put%20them%20all%20through%20a%20process%20of%20lecturing%20because%20they%20need%20to%20verbalise%20the%20information%20in%20their%20head.%20The%20best%20way%20to%20verbalise%20this%20information%20is%20to%20teach.%20So%2C%20they%20become%20pro-bono%20interns%20at%20the%20FMP.%20Following%20this%2C%20I%20conduct%20their%20mock%20interview%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-epautoplay%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20data-facadesrc%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F0trXNLjaynY%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26amp%3Bautoplay%3D0%26amp%3Bcc_load_policy%3D0%26amp%3Bcc_lang_pref%3D%26amp%3Biv_load_policy%3D3%26amp%3Bloop%3D0%26amp%3Bmodestbranding%3D0%26amp%3Brel%3D0%26amp%3Bfs%3D1%26amp%3Bplaysinline%3D1%26amp%3Bautohide%3D2%26amp%3Btheme%3Ddark%26amp%3Bcolor%3Dred%26amp%3Bcontrols%3D1%26amp%3B%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20data-spai-excluded%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2F0trXNLjaynY%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22YouTube%20player%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELife%20after%20IRS%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20formally%20quitting%20the%20service%20last%20year%2C%20Ravi%20knew%20that%20he%20needed%20to%20find%20a%20way%20of%20not%20just%20sustaining%20himself%20but%20also%20supporting%20the%20FMP.%20As%20a%20res