0leads%20so%20far%2C%20which%20is%20helpful%20for%20young%20lawyers%20to%20gain%20a%20good%20customer%20base%20and%20handle%20a%20variety%20of%20cases.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20found%20the%20company%20through%20social%20media.%20What%20is%20unique%20about%20them%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20they%20give%20you%20verified%20leads%20(clients)%20and%20help%20you%20with%20all%20the%20background%20information.%20They%20give%20you%20a%20pretty%20good%20deal%20and%20think%20about%20the%20welfare%20of%20both%20the%20clients%20and%20the%20lawyers%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Siddhant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%2C%20how%20are%20the%20lawyers%20vetted%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEach%20lawyer%E2%80%99s%20information%20is%20cross%20checked%20with%20the%20bar%20council.%20We%20verify%20their%20credentials%20through%20their%20bar%20council%20number%2C%E2%80%9D%20states%20Shreya.%20The%20lawyers%20using%20the%20website%20have%20an%20experience%20of%20anywhere%20between%20three%20and%20twenty%20years%2C%20bringing%20in%20a%20traffic%20of%20about%20200-300%20customers%20every%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20their%20study%2C%20most%20of%20the%20clients%20on%20Rest%20The%20Case%20are%20using%20assistance%20for%20either%20divorce%20or%20family%20law%20cases%2C%20or%20property%20disputes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20team%20of%2015%2C%20the%20CEO%20is%20looking%20to%20bring%20in%20lawyers%20from%20more%20cities%20across%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20most%20people%20get%20frazzled%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20matters%20of%20the%20court%2C%20the%20ease%20and%20one-on-one%20help%20that%20the%20platform%20provides%20has%20become%20their%20USP.%20%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99ve%20made%20access%20to%20legal%20information%20as%20simple%20as%20clicking%20a%20button%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20lawyer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhy%20appropriate%20exposure%20matters%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5C